msgstr ""
":ref:`Naviger til produktformularen <ecommerce/products/product-creation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:57
msgid ""
"Set the product's :guilabel:`Sales Price` and select the unit "
