msgstr ""
"at konfigurere :ref:`fastpris <inventory/shipping/fixed>`-forsendelse der "
"gælder for alle ordrer;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:64
msgid "to configure shipping :ref:`based on rules <inventory/shipping/rules>`;"
msgstr ""
"at konfigurere forsendelse :ref:`baseret på regler <inventory/shipping/"
