#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:67
msgid ""
"To create a custom :doc:`delivery method </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>`, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Delivery Methods`, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, and :ref:`configure it <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"delivery-product>`."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en tilpasset :doc:`leveringsmetode </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"new_delivery_method>` skal du gå til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> "
"Konfiguration --> Leveringsmetoder`, klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` "
"og :ref:`konfigurere den <inventory/shipping_receiving/delivery-product>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:73
msgid ""
"Upon :ref:`configuring <inventory/shipping_receiving/delivery-product>` a "
