msgstr ""
"Efter :ref:`konfigurering <inventory/shipping_receiving/delivery-product>` "
"af en leveringsmetode kan du:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:76
msgid ""
"Restrict it :doc:`to a specific website <../website/configuration/"
"multi_website>` by selecting it in the :guilabel:`Website` field."
msgstr ""
"Begræns den :doc:`til en specifik hjemmeside <../website/configuration/"
"multi_website>` ved at vælge den i feltet :guilabel:`Website`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:78
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Availability` tab to define :ref:`conditions <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/availability>` for the delivery method based on the "
"order's content or destination."
msgstr ""
"Brug fanen :guilabel:`Availability` til at definere :ref:`betingelser "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/availability>` for leveringsmetoden baseret på "
"ordrens indhold eller destination."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:81
msgid ""
"Enable the :ref:`Cash on Delivery <payment_providers/inperson_payments/"
"cash_on_delivery>` option so customers can pay when their order is delivered."
msgstr ""
"Aktivere :ref:`Efterkrav <payment_providers/inperson_payments/"
"cash_on_delivery>`-muligheden, så kunderne kan betale, når deres ordre "
"leveres."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:83
msgid ""
"Add a :guilabel:`Tracking Link` to allow customer to track their order via "
"the customer portal."
msgstr ""
"Tilføje et :guilabel:`Sporinglink` for at give kunden mulighed for at spore "
"deres ordre via kundeportalen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:88
msgid "Click & Collect"
msgstr "Klik og hent"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:90
msgid ""
"To allow customers to reserve products online and collect them in-store, "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at give kunder mulighed for at reservere produkter online og afhente dem "
"i butikken, skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:93
msgid ""
"Scroll to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, enable :guilabel:`Click & "
"Collect`, and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Rul ned til sektionen :guilabel:`Webshop`, aktiver :guilabel:`Klik & "
"Afhent`, og :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:95
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Pickup Locations` "
"to :doc:`configure the delivery method </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>`, if "
"needed, and ensure the :guilabel:`Provider` field is set to :guilabel:`Pick "
"up in store`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Konfigurer afhentningssteder` for "
"at :doc:`konfigurere leveringsmetoden </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>`, hvis "
"det er nødvendigt, og sørg for, at feltet :guilabel:`Udbyder` er indstillet "
"til :guilabel:`Afhent i butik`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:99
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Stores` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line` and select the "
"warehouse(s) where customers can collect their orders."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Stores` skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Add a line` og vælge "
"det eller de lagre, hvor kunderne kan afhente deres ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:101
msgid ""
"Once the setup is complete, click the :guilabel:`Unpublished` button to "
"change the status to :guilabel:`Published` and make the delivery method "
"available to customers."
msgstr ""
"Når opsætningen er fuldført, skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Ikke "
"offentliggjort` for at ændre status til :guilabel:`Offentliggjort` og gøre "
"leveringsmetoden tilgængelig for kunderne."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:105
msgid ""
"When the product is in stock, a location selector is displayed on "
"the :doc:`product page <configuration/products>` and "
"the :guilabel:`Address` :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` page. "
"Customers cannot select a pick-up location if the product is out of stock at "
"that location, unless the :ref:`Continue selling <ecommerce/products/stock-"
"management>` option for out-of-stock products is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Når produktet er på lager, vises en lokalitetsvælger på :doc:`produktsiden "
"<configuration/products>` og siden :guilabel:`Adresse` under :ref:`checkout "
"<ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`. Kunderne kan ikke vælge et afhentningssted, "
"hvis produktet er udsolgt på det pågældende sted, medmindre :ref:`Fortsæt "
"med at sælge <ecommerce/products/stock-management>`-muligheden for udsolgte "
"produkter er aktiveret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:110
msgid ""
"If the :ref:`Show Available Qty <ecommerce/products/stock-management>` "
"option is enabled for a product, customers can view the stock quantity "
"available for each warehouse in the location selector on the product page."
msgstr ""
"Hvis funktionen :ref:`Show Available Qty <ecommerce/products/stock-"
"management>` er aktiveret for et produkt, kan kunderne se den disponible "
"lagermængde for hvert lager i lokationsvælgeren på produktsiden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:113
msgid ""
"Each warehouse must have a **complete address** to ensure its location is "
"accurately displayed to customers. Incomplete addresses prevent the "
"warehouse from being shown."
msgstr ""
"Hvert lager skal have en **komplet adresse** for at sikre, at dets placering "
"vises korrekt for kunderne. Ufuldstændige adresser forhindrer lageret i at "
"blive vist."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:115
msgid ""
"In a multi-company environment, the company assigned to the warehouse must "
"match the company assigned to the website on which the delivery method is "
"used. If the companies differ, the pickup location cannot be selected."
msgstr ""
"I et flerfirma-miljø skal det firma, der er tildelt til lageret, svare til "
"det firma, der er tildelt til den hjemmeside, hvor leveringsmetoden bruges. "
"Hvis firmaerne er forskellige, kan afhentningsstedet ikke vælges."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:118
msgid "The :guilabel:`Click & Collect` option is not available for services."
msgstr ""
"Muligheden :guilabel:`Klik & Afhent` er ikke tilgængelig for tjenester."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:119
msgid ""
"By default, the :ref:`Pay on Site <payment_providers/inperson_payments/"
"pay_on_site>` payment method is :ref:`enabled and published "
"<payment_providers/add_new>` when the :guilabel:`Click & Collect` feature is "
"activated."
msgstr ""
"Som standard er betalingsmetoden :ref:`Betal på stedet <payment_providers/"
"inperson_payments/pay_on_site>` :ref:`aktiveret og publiceret "
"<payment_providers/add_new>`, når funktionen :guilabel:`Klik & Afhent` er "
"aktiveret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:124
msgid ":ref:`ecommerce/products/stock-management`"
msgstr ":ref:`ecommerce/products/stock-management`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:3
msgid "eLearning"
msgstr "eLearning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **eLearning** app allows you to easily upload content, define learning "
"objectives, manage attendees, assess students' progress, and even set up "
"rewards. Engaging participants in a meaningful learning experience enhances "
"their attentiveness and fosters heightened productivity."
msgstr ""
"Appen **eLearning** giver dig mulighed for nemt at uploade indhold, definere "
"læringsmål, administrere deltagere, vurdere studerendes fremskridt og endda "
"oprette belønninger. At engagere deltagerne i en meningsfuld "
"læringsoplevelse øger deres opmærksomhed og fremmer højere produktivitet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:10
msgid ""
"You can manage your eLearning content on the **front end** or the **back "
"end**. The **front end** allows you to create content quickly from your "
"website, while the **back end** provides additional options and allows "
"collaboration. This documentation focuses on using the back end to create "
"your content."
msgstr ""
"Du kan administrere dit eLearning-indhold på **front end** eller **back "
"end**. **Front end** giver dig mulighed for hurtigt at oprette indhold fra "
"din hjemmeside, mens **back end** giver yderligere muligheder og tillader "
"samarbejde. Denne dokumentation fokuserer på at bruge back end til at "
"oprette dit indhold."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:16
msgid "`Odoo Tutorials: eLearning <https://www.odoo.com/slides/elearning-56>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: eLearning <https://www.odoo.com/slides/elearning-56>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:21
msgid "Courses"
msgstr "Retter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:23
msgid ""
"To get an overview of all courses, go to :menuselection:`eLearning --> "
"Courses --> Courses`."
msgstr ""
"For at få et overblik over alle kurser skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`eLearning --> Courses --> Courses`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click on a course card to edit the course on the back end. "
"Click :guilabel:`View course` to access the course on the front end."
msgstr ""
"Klik på et kursuskort for at redigere kurset i backend. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Vis kursus` for at få adgang til kurset i frontend."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:31
msgid "Course creation"
msgstr "Oprettelse af kursus"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:33
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new course. In the form that opens, add "
"a :guilabel:`Course Title` and one or more :guilabel:`Tags` to categorize "
"the course and :ref:`allow users to filter courses based on their tags "
"<elearning/course-groups>`. To add an image to illustrate the course, hover "
"your mouse on the camera placeholder image and click on :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette et nyt kursus. I formularen, der "
"åbnes, tilføj en :guilabel:`Kursustitel` og en eller flere :guilabel:`Tags` "
"til at kategorisere kurset og :ref:`give brugere mulighed for at filtrere "
"kurser baseret på deres tags <elearning/course-groups>`. For at tilføje et "
"billede til illustration af kurset, hold musen over kameraets "
"pladsholderbillede og klik på :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(Rediger)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:39
msgid ""
"Four tabs allow you to edit your course further: :ref:`Content <elearning/"
"content>`, :ref:`Description <elearning/description>`, :ref:`Options "
"<elearning/options>`, and :ref:`Karma <elearning/karma>`."
msgstr ""
"Fire faner giver dig mulighed for at redigere dit kursus "
"yderligere: :ref:`Indhold <elearning/content>`, :ref:`Beskrivelse <elearning/"
"description>`, :ref:`Indstillinger <elearning/options>` og :ref:`Karma "
"<elearning/karma>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Create your elearning course."
msgstr "Opret dit eLearning-kursus."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:49
msgid "Content tab"
msgstr "Fanen Indhold"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:51
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to manage the course content. Click :guilabel:`Add "
"Section` to divide the course into different sections. Click :guilabel:`Add "
"Content` to create :ref:`content items <elearning/content-creation>`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add Certification` to assess the attendees' level of "
"understanding, certify their skills, and motivate them. **Certification** is "
"part of the :doc:`Surveys <../marketing/surveys/create>` app."
msgstr ""
"Denne fane giver dig mulighed for at administrere kursusindholdet. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj sektion` for at opdele kurset i forskellige sektioner. "
"Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj indhold` for at oprette :ref:`indholdselementer "
"<elearning/content-creation>`. Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj certificering` for "
"at vurdere deltagernes forståelsesniveau, certificere deres færdigheder og "
"motivere dem. **Certificering** er en del af appen :doc:`Undersøgelser <../"
"marketing/surveys/create>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:318
msgid "Description tab"
msgstr "Fanen Beskrivelse"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:62
msgid ""
"You can add a short description or information related to the course in "
"the :guilabel:`Description` tab. It appears under the course title on your "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilføje en kort beskrivelse eller information relateret til kurset i "
"fanen :guilabel:`Beskrivelse`. Den vises under kursustitlen på din "
"hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Add a description to your course."
msgstr "Tilføj en beskrivelse til dit kursus."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:71
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:91
msgid "Options tab"
msgstr "Záložka možnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:73
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Options` tab, different configurations are "
"available: :ref:`Course <elearning/options-course>`, :ref:`Access rights "
"<elearning/options-access-rights>`, :ref:`Communication <elearning/options-"
"communication>` and :ref:`Display <elearning/options-display>`."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Indstillinger` er forskellige konfigurationer "
"tilgængelige: :ref:`Kursus <elearning/options-"
"course>`, :ref:`Adgangsrettigheder <elearning/options-access-"
"rights>`, :ref:`Kommunikation <elearning/options-communication>` "
"og :ref:`Visning <elearning/options-display>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Overview of the Options tab"
msgstr "Oversigt over fanen Indstillinger"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:84
msgid "Course"
msgstr "Ret"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:86
msgid ""
"Assign a :guilabel:`Responsible` user for the course. If you have multiple "
"websites, use the :guilabel:`Website` field to display the course only on "
"the selected website."
msgstr ""
"Tildel en :guilabel:`Ansvarlig` bruger for kurset. Hvis du har flere "
"hjemmesider, skal du bruge feltet :guilabel:`Hjemmeside` til kun at vise "
"kurset på den valgte hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:92
msgid "Access rights"
msgstr "Adgangsrettigheder"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prerequisites`: Set one or more other courses that users are "
"advised to complete before accessing the course."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forudsætninger`: Angiv et eller flere andre kurser, som brugere "
"anbefales at gennemføre, før de får adgang til kurset."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:96
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prerequisite Of`: If the course has been defined as a "
"prerequisite for one or more courses, this read-only field displays the "
"course name(s)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forudsætning for`: Hvis kurset er blevet defineret som en "
"forudsætning for et eller flere kurser, viser dette skrivebeskyttede felt "
"kursusnavnet/-navnene."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:98
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Show course to`: Define who can see the course on your website. "
"Select one of the following:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vis kursus for`: Definer, hvem der kan se kurset på din "
"hjemmeside. Vælg en af følgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:101
msgid ":guilabel:`Everyone`: The course is publicly visible."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Alle`: Kurset er offentligt synligt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Signed In`: The course is only visible to users who are logged in."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Logget ind`: Kurset er kun synligt for brugere, der er logget ind."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:103
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Course Attendees`: The course is only visible to users who are "
"already enrolled in the course."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kursusdeltagere`: Kurset er kun synligt for brugere, der allerede "
"er tilmeldt kurset."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:105
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Anyone with the link`: The course can only be accessed via a "
"direct link."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Alle med linket`: Kurset kan kun tilgås via et direkte link."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Enroll Policy`: Define how people can enroll in the course. The "
"choice of policy also determines which internal eLearning users can add, "
"i.e., manually enroll, attendees via the :guilabel:`Add attendees` button or "
"invite attendees to enroll via the :guilabel:`Invite` button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tilmeldingspolitik`: Angiv, hvordan personer kan tilmelde sig "
"kurset. Valget af politik bestemmer også, hvilke interne eLearning-brugere "
"der kan tilføje, dvs. manuelt tilmelde deltagere via "
"knappen :guilabel:`Tilføj deltagere` eller invitere deltagere til at "
"tilmelde sig via knappen :guilabel:`Inviter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:112
msgid ""
"Internal eLearning users have either `Officer` or `Manager` :doc:`access "
"rights </applications/general/users/access_rights>`."
msgstr ""
"Interne eLearning-brugere har enten `Officer`- eller "
"`Manager`-:doc:`adgangsrettigheder </applications/general/users/"
"access_rights>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:115
msgid "Select one of the following:"
msgstr "Vælg en af følgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:117
msgid ":guilabel:`Open`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Åben`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:119
msgid "Anyone who can see the course can enroll."
msgstr "Alle, der kan se kurset, kan tilmelde sig."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:120
msgid ""
"Any eLearning Officer or eLearning Manager can add or invite internal or "
"external attendees."
msgstr ""
"Enhver eLearning Officer eller eLearning Manager kan tilføje eller invitere "
"interne eller eksterne deltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:123
msgid ":guilabel:`On invitation`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`På invitation`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:125
msgid "Only people who have received an invitation can enroll in the course."
msgstr "Kun personer, der har modtaget en invitation, kan tilmelde sig kurset."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:126
msgid ""
"If the course visibility is set to :guilabel:`Everyone`, :guilabel:`Signed "
"In`, or :guilabel:`Anyone with the link`, any non-invited person who logs in "
"can request access to the course via the course page. Enter "
"an :guilabel:`Enroll Message` to explain how to enroll, e.g., \"Contact "
"Responsible\"."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kursets synlighed er indstillet til :guilabel:`Alle`, :guilabel:`Logget "
"ind` eller :guilabel:`Alle med linket`, kan enhver ikke-inviteret person, "
"der logger ind, anmode om adgang til kurset via kursets side. Indtast "
"en :guilabel:`Tilmeldingsbesked` for at forklare, hvordan man tilmelder sig, "
"f.eks. \"Kontakt ansvarlig\"."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:132
msgid ""
"The request creates a to-do assigned to the course's :guilabel:`Responsible` "
"user, allowing them to :guilabel:`Grant Access` or :guilabel:`Refuse "
"Access`. The to-do is visible to the :guilabel:`Responsible` user and any "
"eLearning Manager in the course's chatter, and the :guilabel:`Responsible` "
"user is notified via email. Either the :guilabel:`Responsible` user or an "
"eLearning Manager can grant access, in which case the requestor is "
"automatically enrolled in the course, or refuse access."
msgstr ""
"Anmodningen opretter et gøremål tildelt kursets :guilabel:`Ansvarlige`-"
"bruger, hvilket giver dem mulighed for at :guilabel:`Give adgang` "
"eller :guilabel:`Afvise adgang`. Gøremålet er synligt for "
"den :guilabel:`Ansvarlige`-bruger og enhver eLearning Manager i kursets "
"chatter, og den :guilabel:`Ansvarlige`-bruger bliver underrettet via e-mail. "
"Enten den :guilabel:`Ansvarlige`-bruger eller en eLearning Manager kan give "
"adgang, hvorefter anmoderen automatisk tilmeldes kurset, eller afvise adgang."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:139
msgid ""
"Only the :guilabel:`Responsible` user for the course or an eLearning Manager "
"can add or invite internal or external attendees."
msgstr ""
"Kun den :guilabel:`Ansvarlige`-bruger for kurset eller en eLearning Manager "
"kan tilføje eller invitere interne eller eksterne deltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:142
msgid ":guilabel:`On payment`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ved betaling`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:144
msgid ""
"This option is only shown if the :guilabel:`Paid courses` feature is enabled "
"in the :ref:`eLearning settings <elearning/settings>`."
msgstr ""
"Denne mulighed vises kun, hvis funktionen :guilabel:`Betalte kurser` er "
"aktiveret i :ref:`eLearning-indstillingerne <elearning/settings>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:146
msgid "Anyone who can see the course can enroll in the course upon payment."
msgstr "Alle, der kan se kurset, kan tilmelde sig kurset ved betaling."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:147
msgid ""
"Any eLearning Officer can *invite* internal or external attendees to enroll "
"in the course."
msgstr ""
"Enhver eLearning Officer kan *invitere* interne eller eksterne deltagere til "
"at tilmelde sig kurset."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:148
msgid ""
"Only the :guilabel:`Responsible` user for the course or an eLearning Manager "
"can *add* attendees. Payment is not required when an attendee is added in "
"this way."
msgstr ""
"Kun den :guilabel:`Ansvarlige`-bruger for kurset eller en eLearning Manager "
"kan *tilføje* deltagere. Betaling er ikke påkrævet, når en deltager tilføjes "
"på denne måde."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:150
msgid ""
"To set a course as :guilabel:`On payment`, a :guilabel:`Product` must be "
"selected; only products set up with :guilabel:`Course` as "
"their :guilabel:`Product Type` are available for selection."
msgstr ""
"For at indstille et kursus som :guilabel:`Ved betaling`, skal "
"et :guilabel:`Produkt` vælges; kun produkter, der er opsat "
"med :guilabel:`Kursus` som deres :guilabel:`Produkttype`, er tilgængelige "
"til valg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:155
msgid ""
"To add or invite an attendee, the attendee must be an existing contact or "
"created as a new contact. A person who creates a customer account on your "
"website is automatically a contact."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje eller invitere en deltager skal deltageren være en "
"eksisterende kontakt eller oprettes som en ny kontakt. En person, der "
"opretter en kundekonto på din hjemmeside, er automatisk en kontakt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:161
msgid "Communication"
msgstr "Kommunikation"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:163
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Reviews`: Enable this option to allow attendees to like, "
"comment on, and submit reviews for the course content."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tillad anmeldelser`: Aktiver denne mulighed for at give deltagere "
"mulighed for at synes om, kommentere på og indsende anmeldelser af "
"kursusindholdet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:165
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Forum`: Add a dedicated forum to the course. This option is only "
"shown if the :guilabel:`Forum` feature is enabled in the :ref:`eLearning "
"settings <elearning/settings>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forum`: Tilføj et dedikeret forum til kurset. Denne mulighed "
"vises kun, hvis funktionen :guilabel:`Forum` er aktiveret i :ref:`eLearning-"
"indstillingerne <elearning/settings>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:167
msgid ""
":guilabel:`New Content Notification`: Select an email template to send "
"emails to attendees when you upload new content items. Click on :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`Internal link` to access the email template editor."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Meddelelse om nyt indhold`: Vælg en e-mailskabelon til at sende e-"
"mails til deltagere, når du uploader nye indholdselementer. Klik "
"på :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Internt link` for at åbne e-"
"mailskabelon-editoren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:170
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Completion Notification`: Select an email template to send emails "
"to attendees once they reach the end of the course. Click on :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Internal link` to access the email template editor."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Meddelelse om gennemførelse`: Vælg en e-mailskabelon til at sende "
"e-mails til deltagere, når de når slutningen af kurset. Klik på :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`Internt link` for at åbne e-mailskabelon-editoren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:175
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Mailing` feature is enabled in the :ref:`eLearning "
"settings <elearning/settings>`, it is possible to send mass mailings to "
"people enrolled in a course via a :guilabel:`Contact Attendees` button at "
"the top left of the course form. The button is only visible to eLearning "
"Officers who also have `User` :doc:`access rights </applications/general/"
"users/access_rights>` for Email Marketing and to eLearning Managers."
msgstr ""
"Hvis funktionen :guilabel:`Mailing` er aktiveret i :ref:`eLearning-"
"indstillingerne <elearning/settings>`, er det muligt at sende "
"masseudsendelser til personer tilmeldt et kursus via en :guilabel:`Kontakt "
"deltagere`-knap øverst til venstre på kursusformularen. Knappen er kun "
"synlig for eLearning Officers, der også har "
"`Bruger` :doc:`adgangsrettigheder </applications/general/users/"
"access_rights>` til E-mailmarketing, og for eLearning Managers."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:184
msgid "Display"
msgstr "Vis"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:186
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Training`: The course content appears as a training program, and "
"the courses must be taken in the proposed order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Træning`: Kursusindholdet vises som et træningsprogram, og "
"kurserne skal tages i den foreslåede rækkefølge."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:188
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Documentation`: The content is available in any order. Use "
"the :guilabel:`Featured Content` field to define which content items are "
"promoted on the course homepage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dokumentation`: Indholdet er tilgængeligt i vilkårlig rækkefølge. "
"Brug feltet :guilabel:`Fremhævet indhold` til at definere, hvilke "
"indholdselementer der fremhæves på kursushjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:194
msgid "Karma tab"
msgstr "Karma-fane"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:196
msgid "This tab is about gamification to make eLearning fun and interactive."
msgstr ""
"Denne fane handler om gamification for at gøre eLearning sjovt og "
"interaktivt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:198
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Rewards` section, choose how many karma points you want to "
"grant attendees when they :guilabel:`Review` or :guilabel:`Finish` a course."
msgstr ""
"I afsnittet :guilabel:`Belønninger` skal du vælge, hvor mange karmapoint du "
"vil tildele deltagere, når de :guilabel:`Anmelder` "
"eller :guilabel:`Gennemfører` et kursus."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:201
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Access Rights` section, define the karma points needed "
"to :guilabel:`Add Review`, :guilabel:`Add Comment`, or :guilabel:`Vote` on "
"the course."
msgstr ""
"I afsnittet :guilabel:`Adgangsrettigheder` skal du definere de karmapoint, "
"der er nødvendige for at :guilabel:`Tilføj anmeldelse`, :guilabel:`Tilføj "
"kommentar` eller :guilabel:`Stem` på kurset."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:207
msgid "Course groups"
msgstr "Kursusgrupper"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:209
msgid ""
"**Course Groups** allow users to filter the :guilabel:`All Courses` "
"dashboard on your website and find the course that meets their interests, "
"needs, level, etc."
msgstr ""
"**Kursusgrupper** giver brugere mulighed for at filtrere "
"dashboardet :guilabel:`Alle kurser` på din hjemmeside og finde det kursus, "
"der opfylder deres interesser, behov, niveau osv."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:212
msgid ""
"To manage them, go to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Configuration --> Course "
"Groups`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new course group. Add "
"the :guilabel:`Course Group Name`, enable :guilabel:`Menu Entry` to allow "
"users to search by course group on the website, and add tags in "
"the :guilabel:`Tag Name` column. For each tag, you can select a "
"corresponding color."
msgstr ""
"For at administrere dem skal du gå til :menuselection:`eLearning --> "
"Konfiguration --> Kursusgrupper`. Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette en "
"ny kursusgruppe. Tilføj :guilabel:`Kursusgruppens navn`, "
"aktivér :guilabel:`Menupunkt` for at give brugere mulighed for at søge efter "
"kursusgruppe på hjemmesiden, og tilføj tags i kolonnen :guilabel:`Tagnavn`. "
"For hvert tag kan du vælge en tilsvarende farve."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:220
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Indstillinger"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:222
msgid ""
"The following options are available in the eLearning settings. Go "
"to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Configuration --> Settings`, then enable "
"the desired feature:"
msgstr ""
"Følgende muligheder er tilgængelige i eLearning-indstillingerne. Gå "
"til :menuselection:`eLearning --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og "
"aktivér derefter den ønskede funktion:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:225
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Certifications`: Assess attendees' knowledge and provide official "
"certification of their skills."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Certificeringer`: Vurdér deltagernes viden, og giv officiel "
"certificering af deres færdigheder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:227
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Paid Courses`: Sell course access directly through your website "
"and track revenue."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Betalte kurser`: Sælg kursusadgang direkte via din hjemmeside, og "
"spor indtægter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:230
msgid ""
"Enabling :guilabel:`Paid Courses` automatically installs "
"the :guilabel:`eCommerce` module, which may impact your `pricing plan "
"<https://www.odoo.com/pricing>`_."
msgstr ""
"Aktivering af :guilabel:`Betalte kurser` installerer automatisk "
"modulet :guilabel:`Webshop`, hvilket kan påvirke din `prisplan <https://"
"www.odoo.com/pricing>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:234
msgid ":doc:`eCommerce documentation </applications/websites/ecommerce>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Webshop-dokumentation </applications/websites/ecommerce>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:236
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mailing`: Send mass mailings to keep all attendees informed and "
"up to date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mailing`: Send masseudsendelser for at holde alle deltagere "
"informerede og opdaterede."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:237
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Forum`: Build a community space where attendees can ask questions "
"and help each other."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forum`: Byg et fællesskabsrum, hvor deltagere kan stille "
"spørgsmål og hjælpe hinanden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:242
msgid "Content"
msgstr "Indhold"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:244
msgid ""
"To manage course content, go to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Courses --> "
"Contents`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a content item. Add "
"the :guilabel:`Content Title` and any desired :ref:`Tags <elearning/content-"
"tags>`, then fill in the required information in the different tabs."
msgstr ""
"For at administrere kursusindhold skal du gå til :menuselection:`eLearning --"
"> Kurser --> Indhold`. Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette et "
"indholdselement. Tilføj :guilabel:`indholdstitlen` og eventuelle "
"ønskede :ref:`tags <elearning/content-tags>`, og udfyld derefter de "
"nødvendige oplysninger i de forskellige faner."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Create your content."
msgstr "Opret dit indhold."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:252
msgid ""
"You can also create new content from within a course. Go "
"to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Courses --> Courses`, click the relevant "
"course card, then click :guilabel:`Add content` at the bottom of "
"the :guilabel:`Content` tab."
msgstr ""
"Du kan også oprette nyt indhold inde fra et kursus. Gå "
"til :menuselection:`eLearning --> Kurser --> Kurser`, klik på det relevante "
"kursuskort, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Tilføj indhold` nederst i "
"fanen :guilabel:`Indhold`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:259
msgid "Document tab"
msgstr "Fanen Dokument"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:261
msgid "For each content type, provide the following information:"
msgstr "For hver indholdstype skal du angive følgende oplysninger:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:263
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Course`: Select the course to which the content item belongs."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kursus`: Vælg det kursus, som indholdselementet hører til."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:264
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Content Type`: Select the relevant :ref:`content type <elearning/"
"content-type>` and provide the required information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Indholdstype`: Vælg den relevante :ref:`indholdstype <elearning/"
"content-type>`, og angiv de nødvendige oplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:266
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Responsible`: Select the user responsible for the content item. "
"By default, this is the user who creates the course, but another user can be "
"selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ansvarlig`: Vælg den bruger, der er ansvarlig for "
"indholdselementet. Som standard er dette den bruger, der opretter kurset, "
"men en anden bruger kan vælges."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:268
msgid ":guilabel:`Duration`: Enter the time required to complete the lesson."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Varighed`: Angiv den tid, der kræves for at gennemføre lektionen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:269
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Preview`: Enable this if the content should be accessible "
"to anyone."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tillad forhåndsvisning`: Aktivér dette, hvis indholdet skal være "
"tilgængeligt for alle."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:272
msgid ""
"If the :ref:`Content Type <elearning/content-type>` is :guilabel:`Document`, "
"enabling :guilabel:`Allow Download` allows users to download the content."
msgstr ""
"Hvis :ref:`indholdstypen <elearning/content-type>` er :guilabel:`Dokument`, "
"giver aktivering af :guilabel:`Tillad download` brugerne mulighed for at "
"downloade indholdet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:275
msgid ""
"Two read-only fields provide data about how often the content item is viewed:"
msgstr ""
"To skrivebeskyttede felter viser data om, hvor ofte indholdselementet ses:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:277
msgid ""
":guilabel:`# of Public Views`: displays the number of views from non-"
"enrolled participants."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`# af offentlige visninger`: viser antallet af visninger fra ikke-"
"tilmeldte deltagere."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:278
msgid ""
":guilabel:`# Total Views`: displays the total number of views (non-enrolled "
"and enrolled participants)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`# samlede visninger`: viser det samlede antal visninger (ikke-"
"tilmeldte og tilmeldte deltagere)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Provide information about the content."
msgstr "Angiv oplysninger om indholdet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:287
msgid "Content types"
msgstr "Indholdstyper"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:289
msgid "You can add the following content types:"
msgstr "Du kan tilføje følgende indholdstyper:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:291
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Image`: To upload an image, select :guilabel:`Upload from "
"Device`, click :guilabel:`Upload your file`, then select the relevant file. "
"Supported formats include JPG, JPEG, PNG, SVG, GIF, and WEBP. The maximum "
"file size is 25MB."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Billede`: For at uploade et billede skal du "
"vælge :guilabel:`Upload fra enhed`, klikke på :guilabel:`Upload din fil` og "
"derefter vælge den relevante fil. Understøttede formater inkluderer JPG, "
"JPEG, PNG, SVG, GIF og WEBP. Den maksimale filstørrelse er 25 MB."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:295
msgid ""
"Alternatively, to add an image saved on Google Drive, "
"select :guilabel:`Retrieve from Google Drive`, then add the Google Drive "
"link to the image."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan du tilføje et billede gemt på Google Drev ved at "
"vælge :guilabel:`Hent fra Google Drev` og derefter tilføje Google Drev-"
"linket til billedet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:298
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Article`: Articles are website pages that are customized using "
"the website builder on your website's front end."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Artikel`: Artikler er hjemmesidesider, der tilpasses ved hjælp af "
"websitebyggeren på din hjemmesides front end."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:301
msgid ""
"With the :guilabel:`Course` selected, click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` "
"smart button, then, at the top-right of the screen, click :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)`. Write the article's content and :doc:`customize "
"the page using the website builder </applications/websites/website/"
"web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Med :guilabel:`Course` valgt, klik på smartknappen :guilabel:`Go to "
"Website`, og klik derefter øverst til højre på skærmen på :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)`. Skriv artiklens indhold, og :doc:`tilpas siden "
"med websitebuilderen </applications/websites/website/web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:305
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Document`: To upload a document, select :guilabel:`Upload from "
"Device`, click :guilabel:`Upload your file`, then select the relevant file. "
"Only PDF documents can be uploaded."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Document`: For at uploade et dokument, vælg :guilabel:`Upload "
"from Device`, klik på :guilabel:`Upload your file`, og vælg derefter den "
"relevante fil. Kun PDF-dokumenter kan uploades."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:308
msgid ""
"Alternatively, to add a Google Slides presentation, Google Doc document, or "
"Google Sheets spreadsheet, click :guilabel:`Retrieve from Google Drive` and "
"add the Google Drive link to the file."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan du tilføje en Google Slides-præsentation, Google Doc-"
"dokument eller Google Sheets-regneark ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Retrieve "
"from Google Drive` og tilføje Google Drive-linket til filen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:312
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Video`: Add the YouTube, Google Drive, or Vimeo link to the video."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Video`: Tilføj YouTube-, Google Drive- eller Vimeo-linket til "
"videoen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:313
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quiz`: Open the :ref:`Quiz tab <elearning/content-quiz>` to "
"create a quiz."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Quiz`: Åbn fanen :ref:`Quiz tab <elearning/content-quiz>` for at "
"oprette en quiz."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:320
msgid ""
"Add a description for the content. This text is displayed in "
"the :guilabel:`About` section of the content item on your website."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj en beskrivelse af indholdet. Denne tekst vises i "
"sektionen :guilabel:`About` for indholdet på din hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:326
msgid "Additional Resources tab"
msgstr "Fanen Additional Resources"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:328
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add a link or a file that supports your "
"participants' learning. The resource appears in the course content on your "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Add a line` for at tilføje et link eller en fil, der "
"understøtter dine deltageres læring. Ressourcen vises i kursusindholdet på "
"din hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Additional ressources"
msgstr "Ekstra ressourcer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:337
msgid "Quiz tab"
msgstr "Fanen Quiz"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:339
msgid ""
"From this tab, you can create a quiz to assess your students at the end of "
"the course."
msgstr ""
"Fra denne fane kan du oprette en quiz til at vurdere dine studerende i "
"slutningen af kurset."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:341
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Points Rewards` section allows you to assign karma points "
"based on how many attempts are needed to answer correctly. To create a "
"question, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, enter the :guilabel:`Question Name`, "
"and add possible answers. Mark the correct answer(s) by "
"selecting :guilabel:`Is correct answer`. You can also use "
"the :guilabel:`Comment` field to provide additional information when an "
"answer is selected."
msgstr ""
"Sektionen :guilabel:`Points Rewards` giver dig mulighed for at tildele "
"karmapoint baseret på, hvor mange forsøg der er nødvendige for at svare "
"korrekt. For at oprette et spørgsmål, klik på :guilabel:`Add a line`, "
"indtast :guilabel:`Question Name`, og tilføj mulige svar. Marker det "
"korrekte svar ved at vælge :guilabel:`Is correct answer`. Du kan også bruge "
"feltet :guilabel:`Comment` til at give yderligere information, når et svar "
"vælges."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:350
msgid "Content Tags"
msgstr "Indholds-tags"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:352
msgid ""
"**Content Tags** are visible on the :guilabel:`Contents` dashboard of a "
"course on your website, and can help users identify the kind of content a "
"particular lesson contains, e.g., theory, or exercises."
msgstr ""
"**Content Tags** er synlige på :guilabel:`Contents`-dashboardet for et "
"kursus på din hjemmeside og kan hjælpe brugere med at identificere den type "
"indhold, som en bestemt lektion indeholder, f.eks. teori eller øvelser."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:355
msgid ""
"To manage content tags, go to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Configuration --"
"> Content Tags`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new tag."
msgstr ""
"For at administrere indholdstags, gå til :menuselection:`eLearning --> "
"Configuration --> Content Tags`. Klik på :guilabel:`New` for at oprette et "
"nyt tag."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:361
msgid "Publish courses and content"
msgstr "Publicer kurser og indhold"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:363
msgid ""
"Courses and content items must be published from the front end to be "
"available to your audience. To access the front end, click the :guilabel:`Go "
"to Website` smart button at the top of the course form or an individual "
"content form."
msgstr ""
"Kurser og indhold skal publiceres fra front end for at være tilgængelige for "
"din målgruppe. For at få adgang til front end, klik på "
"smartknappen :guilabel:`Go to Website` øverst på kursusformularen eller en "
"individuel indholdsformular."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:367
msgid "A course and its content items are published separately:"
msgstr "Et kursus og dets indholdselementer publiceres separat:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:369
msgid ""
"To publish a course, access the main course page, then toggle the switch in "
"the upper-right corner from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"For at publicere et kursus, gå til hovedkursussiden, og skift derefter "
"kontakten i øverste højre hjørne fra :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"til :guilabel:`Published`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:371
msgid ""
"To publish individual content items, click on an item to open it, then "
"toggle the switch from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"For at publicere individuelle indholdselementer, klik på et element for at "
"åbne det, og skift derefter kontakten fra :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"til :guilabel:`Published`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Publish your content."
msgstr "Publicer dit indhold."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:378
msgid ""
"When publishing a new course, publish the individual content items before "
"publishing the course itself. Published content is only available to your "
"audience once the course it is part of is published."
msgstr ""
"Når du udgiver et nyt kursus, skal du udgive de enkelte indholdselementer, "
"før du udgiver selve kurset. Udgivet indhold er først tilgængeligt for dit "
"publikum, når det kursus, det er en del af, er udgivet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:382
msgid ""
"To unpublish a course or an individual content item, open the course or "
"item, then toggle the switch from :guilabel:`Published` "
"to :guilabel:`Unpublished`."
msgstr ""
"For at afpublicere et kursus eller et individuelt indholdselement skal du "
"åbne kurset eller elementet og derefter skifte kontakten "
"fra :guilabel:`Udgivet` til :guilabel:`Afpubliceret`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:386
msgid ""
"Unpublishing a course renders the course *and* its content unavailable to "
"your audience."
msgstr ""
"Afpublicering af et kursus gør kurset *og* dets indhold utilgængeligt for "
"dit publikum."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:3
msgid "Forum"
msgstr "Forum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Odoo Forum** is a question-and-answer forum designed with providing "
"customer support in mind. Adding a forum to a website enables you to build a "
"community, encourage engagement, and share knowledge."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Forum** er et spørgsmål-og-svar-forum designet med kundesupport i "
"tankerne. Tilføjelse af et forum til en hjemmeside gør det muligt at opbygge "
"et fællesskab, tilskynde til engagement og dele viden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:12
msgid "Create a forum"
msgstr "Opret et forum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:14
msgid ""
"To create or edit a forum, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --"
"> Forum: Forums`. Click :guilabel:`New` or select an existing forum and "
"configure the following elements."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette eller redigere et forum skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Konfiguration --> Forum: Fora`. Klik "
"på :guilabel:`Ny` eller vælg et eksisterende forum og konfigurer følgende "
"elementer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:17
msgid ":guilabel:`Forum Name`: add the name of the forum."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Forumnavn`: tilføj forummets navn."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:19
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mode`: select :guilabel:`Questions` to enable marking an answer "
"as best, meaning questions then appear as *solved*, "
"or :guilabel:`Discussions` if the feature is not needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tilstand`: vælg :guilabel:`Spørgsmål` for at aktivere markering "
"af et svar som bedst, hvilket betyder, at spørgsmål derefter vises som "
"*løst*, eller :guilabel:`Diskussioner`, hvis funktionen ikke er nødvendig."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:23
msgid ""
"Regardless of the selected mode, only **one answer** per user is allowed on "
"a single post. Commenting multiple times is allowed, however."
msgstr ""
"Uanset den valgte tilstand er kun **ét svar** pr. bruger tilladt på et "
"enkelt indlæg. Det er dog tilladt at kommentere flere gange."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:26
msgid ":guilabel:`Default Sort`: choose how questions are sorted by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Standardsortering`: vælg, hvordan spørgsmål sorteres som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:28
msgid ":guilabel:`Newest`: by latest question posting date"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nyeste`: efter seneste spørgsmåls opslågsdato"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Last Updated`: by latest posting activity date (answers and "
"comments included)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Senest opdateret`: efter seneste opslagsaktivitetsdato (svar og "
"kommentarer inkluderet)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:30
msgid ":guilabel:`Most Voted`: by highest vote tally"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Mest stemt`: efter højeste stemmeoptælling"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:31
msgid ":guilabel:`Relevance`: by post relevancy (determined by a formula)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Relevans`: efter opslagets relevans (bestemt af en formel)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Answered`: by likelihood to be answered (determined by a formula)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Besvaret`: efter sandsynlighed for at blive besvaret (bestemt af "
"en formel)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:35
msgid ""
"Users have several sorting options (total replies, total views, last "
"activity) on the forum front end."
msgstr ""
"Brugere har flere sorteringsmuligheder (samlede svar, samlede visninger, "
"seneste aktivitet) på forummets frontend."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:38
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Privacy`: select :guilabel:`Public` to let anyone view the "
"forum, :guilabel:`Signed In` to make it visible only for signed-in users, "
"or :guilabel:`Some users` to make it visible only for a specific user access "
"group by selecting one :guilabel:`Authorized Group`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privatliv`: vælg :guilabel:`Offentlig` for at lade alle se "
"forummet, :guilabel:`Logget ind` for at gøre det synligt kun for brugere, "
"der er logget ind, eller :guilabel:`Nogle brugere` for at gøre det synligt "
"kun for en specifik brugeradgangsgruppe ved at vælge "
"en :guilabel:`Autoriseret gruppe`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:42
msgid ""
"Next, configure the :ref:`karma gains <forum/karma-gains>` and "
"the :ref:`karma-related rights <forum/karma-related-rights>`."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurer derefter :ref:`karma-point <forum/karma-gains>` og :ref:`karma-"
"relaterede rettigheder <forum/karma-related-rights>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:48
msgid "Karma points"
msgstr "Karma-point"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:50
msgid ""
"Karma points can be given to users based on different forum interactions. "
"They can be used to determine which forum functionalities users can access, "
"from being able to vote on posts to having moderator rights. They are also "
"used to set user :ref:`ranks <forum/ranks>`."
msgstr ""
"Karma-point kan gives til brugere baseret på forskellige foruminteraktioner. "
"De kan bruges til at bestemme, hvilke forumfunktioner brugere kan få adgang "
"til, fra at kunne stemme på indlæg til at have moderatorrettigheder. De "
"bruges også til at indstille bruger:ref:`rang <forum/ranks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:55
msgid ""
"A user's karma points are shared across all forums, courses, etc., of a "
"single Odoo website."
msgstr ""
"En brugers karmapoint deles på tværs af alle fora, kurser osv. på en enkelt "
"Odoo-hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:56
msgid ""
"eLearning users can earn karma points through different :ref:`course "
"interactions <elearning/karma>` and by :ref:`completing quizzes <elearning/"
"content-quiz>`."
msgstr ""
"eLearning-brugere kan optjene karmapoint gennem "
"forskellige :ref:`kursusinteraktioner <elearning/karma>` og ved "
"at :ref:`gennemføre quizzer <elearning/content-quiz>`."

