#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:103
msgid "Publishing/unpublishing pages"
msgstr "Publikování/zrušení publikování stránek"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:105
msgid ""
"Pages need to be published to make them visible to website visitors. To "
"publish or unpublish a page, access it and toggle the switch in the upper-"
"right corner from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`, or vice "
"versa."
msgstr ""
"Stránky musí být publikovány, aby byly viditelné pro návštěvníky webu. Pro "
"publikování nebo zrušení publikování stránky k ní přistupte a přepněte "
"tlačítko v pravém horním rohu z :guilabel:`Nepublikováno` "
"na :guilabel:`Publikováno` nebo naopak."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:None
msgid "Unpublished/Published toggle"
msgstr "Přepínač Nepublikováno/Publikováno"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:113
msgid "It is also possible to:"
msgstr "Je také možné:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:115
msgid ""
"Publish/unpublish a page from the :ref:`page properties <website/pages/"
"page_properties>`."
msgstr ""
"Publicer/afpublicer en side fra :ref:`sideegenskaber <website/pages/"
"page_properties>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:116
msgid ""
"Publish/unpublish several pages at once. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`, select the pages, then "
"click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` and select :icon:`fa-"
"globe` :guilabel:`Publish` or :icon:`fa-chain-broken` :guilabel:`Unpublish`."
msgstr ""
"Publicer/afpublicer flere sider på én gang. For at gøre dette skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Site --> Sider`, vælge siderne og "
"derefter klikke på :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Handlinger` og vælge :icon:`fa-"
"globe` :guilabel:`Publicer` eller :icon:`fa-chain-"
"broken` :guilabel:`Afpublicer`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:123
msgid "Page properties"
msgstr "Vlastnosti stránky"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:125
msgid ""
"To modify a :ref:`static page's <website/pages/page_type>` properties, "
"access the page you wish to modify, then go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Site --> Properties`, where the following properties can be adapted:"
msgstr ""
"For at ændre egenskaberne for en :ref:`statisk side <website/pages/"
"page_type>` skal du åbne den side, du ønsker at ændre, og derefter gå "
"til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Site --> Egenskaber`, hvor følgende "
"egenskaber kan tilpasses:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:129
msgid ":guilabel:`Page Title`: Modify the page's title."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Sidetitel`: Rediger sidens titel."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Page URL`: Modify the page URL in the field. In this case, you "
"can redirect the old URL to the new one if needed. To do so, "
"enable :guilabel:`Redirect Old URL`, then select the :guilabel:`Type` "
"of :ref:`redirection <website/pages/URL-redirection>`:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Side-URL`: Rediger side-URL'en i feltet. I dette tilfælde kan du "
"omdirigere den gamle URL til den nye, hvis det er nødvendigt. For at gøre "
"dette skal du aktivere :guilabel:`Omdiriger gammel URL`, og derefter "
"vælge :guilabel:`Type` af :ref:`omdirigering <website/pages/URL-"
"redirection>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`301 Moved permanently`: to redirect the page permanently."
msgstr ":guilabel:`301 Trvale přesunuto`: pro trvalé přesměrování stránky."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:135
msgid ":guilabel:`302 Moved temporarily`: to redirect the page temporarily."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`302 Midlertidigt flyttet`: for at omdirigere siden midlertidigt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`In Menu`: Disable if the page should not appear in the menu. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Edit Menu` link to modify the "
"menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`I menu`: Deaktiver, hvis siden ikke skal vises i menuen. Klik "
"på :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Rediger menu`-linket for at redigere "
"menuen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:139
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is Homepage`: Enable if the *static* page should serve as the "
"homepage of the website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Er startside`: Aktiver, hvis den *statiske* side skal fungere som "
"hjemmesidens forside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:140
msgid ":guilabel:`Published`: Enable it to publish the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Udgivet`: Aktiver for at udgive siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:141
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Publishing Date`: To publish the page at a specific date and "
"time, click the field, set the date and time, then press **Enter** or "
"click :guilabel:`Apply` to validate the selection."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Udgivelsesdato`: For at udgive siden på en bestemt dato og "
"tidspunkt skal du klikke på feltet, indstille dato og tidspunkt, derefter "
"trykke på **Enter** eller klikke på :guilabel:`Anvend` for at bekræfte "
"valget."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:143
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Indexed`: Disable if the page should not appear in search engine "
"results."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Indekseret`: Deaktiver, hvis siden ikke skal vises i "
"søgemaskiners resultater."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:144
msgid ":guilabel:`Visibility`: Select who can access the page:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Synlighed`: Vælg, hvem der kan få adgang til siden:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:146
msgid ":guilabel:`Public`: Everyone can access the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Offentlig`: Alle kan få adgang til siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:147
msgid ":guilabel:`Signed In`: Only signed-in users can access the page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Logget ind`: Kun brugere, der er logget ind, kan få adgang til "
"siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:148
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Restricted Group`: Select the :doc:`user access group(s) </"
"applications/general/users/access_rights>` in the :guilabel:`Authorized "
"Groups` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Begrænset gruppe`: Vælg :doc:`brugeradgangsgruppe(r) </"
"applications/general/users/access_rights>` i feltet :guilabel:`Autoriserede "
"grupper`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:150
msgid ""
":guilabel:`With Password`: Type the password required to access the page in "
"the :guilabel:`Password` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Med adgangskode`: Indtast den adgangskode, der kræves for at få "
"adgang til siden, i feltet :guilabel:`Adgangskode`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is a Template`: Toggle the switch to save the page as a template. "
"It is now available in the :guilabel:`Custom` category when :ref:`creating a "
"new page <website/pages/page_creation>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Er en skabelon`: Slå kontakten til for at gemme siden som "
"skabelon. Den er nu tilgængelig i kategorien :guilabel:`Brugerdefineret`, "
"når du :ref:`opretter en ny side <website/pages/page_creation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:159
msgid "Duplicating pages"
msgstr "Duplikere sider"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:161
msgid ""
"To duplicate a page, access the page, then go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Site --> Properties`, and click :guilabel:`Duplicate Page`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Confirmation` window, enter a :guilabel:`Page Name`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Ok`. By default, the new page is not published; it is added "
"after the originally duplicated page in the menu. Use the :doc:`menu editor "
"<header_footer>` to remove it from the menu or change its position."
msgstr ""
"For at duplikere en side skal du åbne siden og derefter gå "
"til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Websted --> Egenskaber` og klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Dupliker side`. I vinduet :guilabel:`Bekræftelse` skal du "
"indtaste et :guilabel:`Sidenavn` og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Ok`. Som "
"standard er den nye side ikke udgivet; den tilføjes efter den oprindeligt "
"duplikerede side i menuen. Brug :doc:`menueditoren <header_footer>` til at "
"fjerne den fra menuen eller ændre dens placering."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:168
msgid ""
"You can also duplicate one or several pages by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`. Select the relevant page(s), "
"click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions`, and select :icon:`fa-files-"
"o` :guilabel:`Duplicate`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan også duplikere en eller flere sider ved at gå "
"til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Websted --> Sider`. Vælg den/de relevante "
"side(r), klik på :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Handlinger`, og vælg :icon:`fa-"
"files-o` :guilabel:`Dupliker`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:175
msgid "Deleting pages"
msgstr "Slette sider"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:177
msgid "To delete a page, proceed as follows:"
msgstr "Sådan sletter du en side:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:179
msgid ""
"Access the page, then go to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Properties` "
"and click :guilabel:`Delete Page`."
msgstr ""
"Åbn siden, gå derefter til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Websted --> "
"Egenskaber` og klik på :guilabel:`Slet side`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:181
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Delete Page` pop-up shows all links referring to the page you "
"want to delete, organized by category. To ensure website visitors do not "
"land on an error page, update all links on the website that refer to the "
"page. To do so, expand a category, then click on a link to open it in a new "
"window. Alternatively, you can set up a :ref:`redirection <website/pages/URL-"
"redirection>` for the deleted page."
msgstr ""
"Pop-op'en :guilabel:`Slet side` viser alle links, der henviser til den side, "
"du vil slette, organiseret efter kategori. For at sikre, at besøgende ikke "
"lander på en fejlside, skal du opdatere alle links på hjemmesiden, der "
"henviser til siden. For at gøre dette skal du udvide en kategori og derefter "
"klikke på et link for at åbne det i et nyt vindue. Alternativt kan du "
"opsætte en :ref:`omdirigering <website/pages/URL-redirection>` for den "
"slettede side."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:186
msgid ""
"Once you have updated the links (or set up a :ref:`redirect <website/pages/"
"URL-redirection>`), tick the :guilabel:`I am sure about this.` checkbox, "
"then click :guilabel:`Delete`."
msgstr ""
"Når du har opdateret links (eller opsat en :ref:`omdirigering <website/pages/"
"URL-redirection>`), skal du markere afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Jeg er "
"sikker på dette.` og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Slet`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:190
msgid ""
"You can also delete one or several pages by going to :menuselection:`Website "
"--> Site --> Pages`. Select the relevant page(s), click :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions`, and select :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Delete`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan også slette en eller flere sider ved at gå "
"til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Websted --> Sider`. Vælg den/de relevante "
"side(r), klik på :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Handlinger`, og vælg :icon:`fa-"
"trash` :guilabel:`Slet`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:197
msgid "URL redirect mapping"
msgstr "URL-omdirigeringstilknytning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:199
msgid ""
"URL redirect mapping involves sending visitors and search engines to a URL "
"other than the one they initially requested. This technique is used, for "
"example, to prevent broken links when :ref:`deleting a page <website/pages/"
"delete-page>`, :ref:`modifying its URL <website/pages/page_properties>`, or "
"migrating the site from another platform to an Odoo :doc:`domain <../"
"configuration/domain_names>`. It can also be used to improve :doc:`seo`."
msgstr ""
"URL-omdirigeringstilknytning indebærer at sende besøgende og søgemaskiner "
"til en anden URL end den, de oprindeligt anmodede om. Denne teknik bruges "
"for eksempel til at forhindre døde links, når man :ref:`sletter en side "
"<website/pages/delete-page>`, :ref:`ændrer dens URL <website/pages/"
"page_properties>`, eller migrerer webstedet fra en anden platform til et "
"Odoo-:doc:`domæne <../configuration/domain_names>`. Den kan også bruges til "
"at forbedre :doc:`seo`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:206
msgid ""
"A redirect record is added automatically every time you :ref:`modify a "
"page's URL <website/pages/page_properties>` and enable :guilabel:`Redirect "
"Old URL`."
msgstr ""
"En omdirigeringspost tilføjes automatisk, hver gang du :ref:`ændrer en sides "
"URL <website/pages/page_properties>` og aktiverer :guilabel:`Omdirigér "
"gammel URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:208
msgid ""
"Redirections can be configured for :ref:`static and dynamic pages <website/"
"pages/page_type>`."
msgstr ""
"Omdirigeringer kan konfigureres for :ref:`statiske og dynamiske sider "
"<website/pages/page_type>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:210
msgid ""
"To access existing URL redirections and create new ones, :doc:`activate the "
"developer mode </applications/general/developer_mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Redirects`. To create a "
"redirection, click :guilabel:`New` in the :guilabel:`Rewrite` view, then "
"adapt the fields:"
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til eksisterende URL-omdirigeringer og oprette nye skal "
"du :doc:`aktivere udviklertilstand </applications/general/developer_mode>` "
"og gå til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Konfiguration --> Omdirigeringer`. "
"For at oprette en omdirigering skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` i "
"visningen :guilabel:`Omskriv` og derefter tilpasse felterne:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:215
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: Enter a name to identify the redirect."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Navn`: Indtast et navn til at identificere omdirigeringen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:216
msgid ":guilabel:`Action`: Select the type of redirection:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Handling`: Vælg typen af omdirigering:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:218
msgid ""
":guilabel:`404 Not found`: Visitors land on a 404 error page when they try "
"to access an unpublished or deleted page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`404 Ikke fundet`: Besøgende lander på en 404-fejlside, når de "
"forsøger at få adgang til en ikke-udgivet eller slettet side."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:220
msgid ""
":guilabel:`301 Moved permanently`: for permanent redirections of unpublished "
"or deleted :ref:`static pages <website/pages/page_type>`. The new URL is "
"shown in search engine results, and the redirect is cached by browsers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`301 Flyttet permanent`: til permanente omdirigeringer af ikke-"
"udgivne eller slettede :ref:`statiske sider <website/pages/page_type>`. Den "
"nye URL vises i søgemaskiners resultater, og omdirigeringen caches af "
"browsere."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:223
msgid ""
":guilabel:`302 Moved temporarily`: for short-term redirections, for example, "
"if you are redesigning or updating a page. The new URL is neither cached by "
"browsers nor shown in search engine results."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`302 Moved temporarily`: til kortvarige omdirigeringer, f.eks. "
"hvis du redesigner eller opdaterer en side. Den nye URL caches hverken af "
"browsere eller vises i søgemaskiners resultater."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:226
msgid ""
":guilabel:`308 Redirect / Rewrite`: for permanent redirections where the "
"original URL is rewritten (typically used for :ref:`dynamic pages <website/"
"pages/page_type>`). The URL is renamed; the new name appears in search "
"engine results and is cached by browsers. Use this redirect type to rename a "
"dynamic page, for example, if you wish to rename `/shop` into `/market`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`308 Redirect / Rewrite`: til permanente omdirigeringer, hvor den "
"oprindelige URL omskrives (bruges typisk til :ref:`dynamiske sider <website/"
"pages/page_type>`). URL'en omdøbes; det nye navn vises i søgemaskiners "
"resultater og caches af browsere. Brug denne omdirigeringstype til at omdøbe "
"en dynamisk side, f.eks. hvis du ønsker at omdøbe `/shop` til `/market`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:232
msgid ""
":guilabel:`URL from`: Enter the URL to be redirected (e.g., `/about-the-"
"company`) or search for the desired :ref:`dynamic page <website/pages/"
"page_type>` and select it from the list."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`URL fra`: Indtast URL'en, der skal omdirigeres (f.eks. `/om-"
"virksomheden`), eller søg efter den ønskede :ref:`dynamiske side <website/"
"pages/page_type>` og vælg den fra listen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:234
msgid ""
":guilabel:`URL to`: For 301, 302, and 308 redirects, enter the URL to be "
"redirected to. If you want to redirect to an external URL, include the "
"protocol (e.g., `https://`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`URL til`: For 301-, 302- og 308-omdirigeringer skal du indtaste "
"den URL, der skal omdirigeres til. Hvis du vil omdirigere til en ekstern "
"URL, skal du inkludere protokollen (f.eks. `https://`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:236
msgid ":guilabel:`Website`: Select a specific website."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Hjemmeside`: Vælg en specifik hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:237
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Active`: Toggle the switch off to deactivate the redirection."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Active`: Slå kontakten fra for at deaktivere omdirigeringen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:238
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sequence`: To define the order in which redirections are "
"performed, e.g., in the case of redirect chains (i.e., a series of redirects "
"where one URL is redirected to another one, which is itself further "
"redirected to another URL)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rækkefølge`: For at definere den rækkefølge, som omdirigeringer "
"udføres i, f.eks. i tilfælde af omdirigeringskæder (dvs. en serie af "
"omdirigeringer, hvor én URL omdirigeres til en anden, som i sig selv "
"omdirigeres videre til en anden URL)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:243
msgid ""
"301 and 302 redirects are commonly used to redirect traffic "
"from :ref:`unpublished <website/pages/un-publish-page>` or :ref:`deleted "
"<website/pages/delete-page>` *static* pages to new pages. The 308 redirect "
"is typically used for permanent URL rewrites, especially for *dynamic* "
"pages. A 404 status is used when a page no longer exists, and no redirection "
"is configured."
msgstr ""
"301- og 302-omdirigeringer bruges almindeligvis til at omdirigere trafik "
"fra :ref:`ikke-publicerede <website/pages/un-publish-page>` "
"eller :ref:`slettede <website/pages/delete-page>` *statiske* sider til nye "
"sider. 308-omdirigeringen bruges typisk til permanente URL-omskrivninger, "
"særligt for *dynamiske* sider. En 404-status bruges, når en side ikke "
"længere eksisterer, og ingen omdirigering er konfigureret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:250
msgid ""
"`Google documentation on redirects and search <https://developers.google.com/"
"search/docs/crawling-indexing/301-redirects>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Googles dokumentation om omdirigeringer og søgning<https://"
"developers.google.com/search/docs/crawling-indexing/301-redirects>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:251
msgid ":doc:`seo`"
msgstr ":doc:`seo`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:5
msgid ""
"Search Engine Optimization, often abbreviated as SEO, is a digital marketing "
"strategy to improve a website's visibility and ranking in search engine "
"results (e.g., in Google). It involves optimizing various elements on your "
"website, including its content, social sharing, URLs, images, and page speed."
msgstr ""
"Søgemaskineoptimering, ofte forkortet SEO, er en digital marketingstrategi "
"til at forbedre en hjemmesides synlighed og rangering i "
"søgemaskineresultater (f.eks. i Google). Det indebærer optimering af "
"forskellige elementer på din hjemmeside, herunder dens indhold, social "
"deling, URL'er, billeder og sidehastighed."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:11
msgid ""
"Several modules are provided to help build the website's content, such "
"as :doc:`eCommerce <../../ecommerce>`, :doc:`Blog <../../"
"blog>`, :doc:`eLearning <../../elearning>`, and :doc:`Forum <../../forum>`."
msgstr ""
"Flere moduler leveres til at hjælpe med at opbygge hjemmesidens indhold, "
"såsom :doc:`Webshop <../../ecommerce>`, :doc:`Blog <../../"
"blog>`, :doc:`eLearning <../../elearning>` og :doc:`Forum <../../forum>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:14
msgid ""
"All provided :doc:`themes <../web_design/themes>` are built with the "
"`Bootstrap <https://getbootstrap.com/>`_ CSS framework to ensure responsive "
"layouts across desktop, tablet, or mobile, which can support SEO."
msgstr ""
"Alle medfølgende :doc:`temaer <../web_design/themes>` er bygget med "
"`Bootstrap <https://getbootstrap.com/>`_ CSS-frameworket for at sikre "
"responsive layouts på tværs af desktop, tablet eller mobil, hvilket kan "
"understøtte SEO."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:19
msgid ""
"`Magic Sheet - Optimize your website [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/"
"folders/1Ywip4tWF2DPkcBaEbeXJxIZg2CjkwKgb>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Magic Sheet - Optimer din hjemmeside [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/"
"folders/1Ywip4tWF2DPkcBaEbeXJxIZg2CjkwKgb>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:23
msgid "Content optimization"
msgstr "Optimering af indhold"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:25
msgid ""
"To optimize a webpage's SEO, access the page, then go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Optimize SEO`."
msgstr ""
"For at optimere en websides SEO skal du gå til siden og derefter "
"til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Websted --> Optimer SEO`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:None
msgid "Search Engine Optimization"
msgstr "Søgemaskineoptimering"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:32
msgid ""
"Changing the title of a blog post or the name of a product automatically "
"updates the link to the related webpage. The old link still functions as "
"a :ref:`301 redirect <website/pages/URL-redirection>` is created, "
"maintaining the SEO."
msgstr ""
"Ændring af titlen på et blogindlæg eller navnet på et produkt opdaterer "
"automatisk linket til den relaterede webside. Det gamle link fungerer "
"stadig, da en :ref:`301-omdirigering <website/pages/URL-redirection>` "
"oprettes, hvilket bevarer SEO."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:37
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Fill with AI` to automatically generate a meta title, a "
"description, and get keyword suggestions."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Udfyld med KI` for automatisk at generere en metatitel, "
"en beskrivelse og få nøgleordsforslag."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:39
msgid ""
"Remove incorrect URLs from the :guilabel:`Broken Link` field and select "
"valid ones to prevent errors."
msgstr ""
"Fjern ukorrekte URL'er fra feltet :guilabel:`Dødt link`, og vælg gyldige for "
"at forhindre fejl."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:43
msgid "Keywords and meta tags"
msgstr "Nøgleord og meta-tags"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:45
msgid "There are two types of keywords in SEO, which serve different purposes."
msgstr "Der er to typer nøgleord i SEO, som tjener forskellige formål."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:48
msgid "In-text keywords"
msgstr "Nøgleord i teksten"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:50
msgid ""
"In-text keywords appear naturally throughout a page’s visible content "
"(titles, headings, and body text) and help search engines determine the "
"topic and relevance of the page. These keywords have a real impact on "
"ranking. They cannot be edited in the :guilabel:`optimize SEO` pop-up."
msgstr ""
"Nøgleord i teksten vises naturligt gennem en sides synlige indhold (titler, "
"overskrifter og brødtekst) og hjælper søgemaskiner med at bestemme emnet og "
"relevansen af siden. Disse nøgleord har en reel indvirkning på rangering. De "
"kan ikke redigeres i pop-up'en :guilabel:`optimere SEO`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:55
msgid "It is strongly recommended to only use one H1 title per page for SEO."
msgstr ""
"Det anbefales stærkt kun at bruge én H1-titel per side af hensyn til SEO."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:60
msgid "Meta tags and meta keywords"
msgstr "Meta-tags og meta-nøgleord"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:62
msgid ""
"**Meta tags** are HTML elements that provide information about a webpage to "
"search engines and website visitors. They play a crucial role in SEO by "
"helping search engines understand the content and context of a webpage and "
"attract visitors with appealing content. They can be edited in "
"the :guilabel:`optimize SEO` pop-up. There are two types of meta tags:"
msgstr ""
"**Metatags** er HTML-elementer, der giver information om en webside til "
"søgemaskiner og besøgende på hjemmesiden. De spiller en afgørende rolle i "
"SEO ved at hjælpe søgemaskiner med at forstå indholdet og konteksten af en "
"webside og tiltrække besøgende med tiltalende indhold. De kan redigeres i "
"pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`optimer SEO`. Der er to typer metatags:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Title` tags specify a webpage's title and are displayed as a "
"clickable link in search engine results. They should be concise, "
"descriptive, and relevant to the page's content. You can update the title "
"tag of your webpage or keep it empty to use the default value based on the "
"page’s content."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Titel`-tags angiver en websides titel og vises som et klikbart "
"link i søgemaskiners resultater. De skal være korte, beskrivende og "
"relevante for sidens indhold. Du kan opdatere din websides titeltag eller "
"lade den være tom for at bruge standardværdien baseret på sidens indhold."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description` tags summarize the webpage's content, often "
"displayed in search engine results below the title. They are used to "
"encourage the user to visit the page. Update the description tag of the "
"webpage, or keep it empty to use the default description based on the page's "
"content."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Beskrivelse`-tags opsummerer websidets indhold, ofte vist i "
"søgemaskiners resultater under titlen. De bruges til at opfordre brugeren "
"til at besøge siden. Opdater beskrivelsestag'et for websiden, eller lad det "
"være tomt for at bruge standardbeskrivelsen baseret på sidens indhold."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:78
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Preview` card displays how the title and description tags "
"should appear in search results. It also includes the URL of your page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forhåndsvisning`-kortet viser, hvordan titel- og "
"beskrivelsestagsene bør fremstå i søgeresultater. Det inkluderer også URL'en "
"til din side."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:81
msgid ""
"**Meta keywords** are placed in a hidden HTML tag `<meta "
"name=\"keywords\">`. Once used to describe a page’s topic, this tag is now "
"ignored by major search engines and has little or no impact on SEO. To "
"edit :guilabel:`Keywords`, enter the keywords you consider essential in this "
"field and click :guilabel:`Add` to see how they are used at different levels "
"in your content (H1, H2, page title, page description, page content) and the "
"related searches in Google. The tool also suggests relevant keywords."
msgstr ""
"**Meta-nøgleord** placeres i et skjult HTML-tag `<meta name=\"keywords\">`. "
"Dette tag blev tidligere brugt til at beskrive en sides emne, men ignoreres "
"nu af store søgemaskiner og har lille eller ingen indvirkning på SEO. For at "
"redigere :guilabel:`Nøgleord`, indtast de nøgleord du anser for væsentlige i "
"dette felt og klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj` for at se hvordan de bruges på "
"forskellige niveauer i dit indhold (H1, H2, sidetitel, sidebeskrivelse, "
"sideindhold) og de relaterede søgninger i Google. Værktøjet foreslår også "
"relevante nøgleord."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:91
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:64
msgid "Images"
msgstr "Billeder"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:93
msgid ""
"The size of images has a significant impact on page speed, which is an "
"essential criterion for search engines to optimize SEO ranking."
msgstr ""
"Billedernes størrelse har en betydelig indflydelse på sidehastigheden, som "
"er et væsentligt kriterium for søgemaskiner til optimering af SEO-rangering."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:97
msgid ""
"Compare how your website ranks using `Google Page Speed <https://"
"pagespeed.web.dev/?utm_source=psi&utm_medium=redirect>`_ or `Pingdom Website "
"Speed Test <https://tools.pingdom.com/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Sammenlign, hvordan din hjemmeside rangerer ved hjælp af `Google Page Speed "
"<https://pagespeed.web.dev/?utm_source=psi&utm_medium=redirect>`_ eller "
"`Pingdom Website Speed Test <https://tools.pingdom.com/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:100
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically compresses uploaded images and converts them to `Webp`. "
"With this file format, photos are smaller, which increases the page loading "
"speed and, therefore, gives a better ranking in SEO. All images used in Odoo "
"official :doc:`themes <../web_design/themes>` are also compressed by default."
msgstr ""
"Odoo komprimerer automatisk uploadede billeder og konverterer dem til "
"`Webp`. Med dette filformat er fotos mindre, hvilket øger "
"sideindlæsningshastigheden og derfor giver en bedre placering i SEO. Alle "
"billeder, der bruges i Odoo officielle :doc:`temaer <../web_design/themes>`, "
"er også komprimeret som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:106
msgid "Third-party themes may not compress images efficiently."
msgstr "Tredjepartstemaer komprimerer muligvis ikke billeder effektivt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:109
msgid ""
"**To modify an image** from a webpage, select the image, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit`, then go to the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, and adapt "
"the :guilabel:`Format` in the :guilabel:`Image` section."
msgstr ""
"**For at ændre et billede** fra en webside skal du vælge billedet, klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Rediger`, derefter gå til fanen :guilabel:`Tilpas` og "
"tilpasse :guilabel:`Format` i afsnittet :guilabel:`Billede`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:113
msgid ""
"Alt tags are used to provide context to what an image is displaying, "
"informing search engine crawlers and allowing them to index an image "
"correctly. Adding alt tags keywords in the :guilabel:`Description` field is "
"essential from an SEO perspective. This description is added to the HTML "
"code of your image, and it is shown when the image cannot be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Alt-tags bruges til at give kontekst om, hvad et billede viser, informere "
"søgemaskinecrawlere og gøre det muligt for dem at indeksere et billede "
"korrekt. Tilføjelse af alt-tags søgeord i feltet :guilabel:`Beskrivelse` er "
"essentielt fra et SEO-perspektiv. Denne beskrivelse tilføjes til HTML-koden "
"for dit billede, og den vises, når billedet ikke kan vises."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:119
msgid "Image for social share"
msgstr "Billede til deling på sociale medier"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:121
msgid ""
"When you share a page on social media, the website logo is selected by "
"default. Search the :doc:`Unsplash image library <../../../general/"
"integrations/unsplash>` or upload any other image by clicking the :icon:`fa-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(upload)` button."
msgstr ""
"Når du deler en side på sociale medier, vælges hjemmesidens logo som "
"standard. Søg i :doc:`Unsplash-billedbiblioteket <../../../general/"
"integrations/unsplash>`, eller upload et andet billede ved at klikke på "
"knappen :icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`(upload)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:126
msgid ""
"To set a default social share image, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Tracking & SEO` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Default Social Share Image`."
msgstr ""
"For at indstille et standard billede til deling på sociale medier skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. Under "
"afsnittet :guilabel:`Sporing & SEO` skal du aktivere :guilabel:`Standard "
"billede til deling på sociale medier`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:131
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Social Preview` card displays how the page's information "
"would appear when shared."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Social forhåndsvisning`-kortet viser, hvordan sidens information "
"vil fremstå, når den deles."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:135
msgid "Indexation"
msgstr "Indeksering"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:137
msgid ""
"Website indexation is the process by which search engines, such as Google, "
"discover, analyze, and store information about a website's content in their "
"database. Search engine bots, known as crawlers or spiders, visit web pages "
"and follow links to collect data, including text, images, and other media. "
"The purpose of indexation is to make a website's content searchable and "
"discoverable to users. Without being indexed, a website or a specific page "
"on that site will not appear in search engine results, regardless of how "
"relevant or well-designed it is. Indexation is a fundamental step "
"in :abbr:`SEO (Search Engine Optimization)`, serving as the foundation for a "
"website's visibility and organic traffic."
msgstr ""
"Hjemmeside-indeksering er den proces hvorved søgemaskiner, såsom Google, "
"opdager, analyserer og gemmer information om en hjemmesides indhold i deres "
"database. Søgemaskinebots, kendt som crawlere eller spindlere, besøger "
"websider og følger links for at indsamle data, herunder tekst, billeder og "
"andre medier. Formålet med indeksering er at gøre en hjemmesides indhold "
"søgbart og synligt for brugere. Uden at være indekseret vil en hjemmeside "
"eller en specifik side på det pågældende site ikke vises i søgemaskiners "
"resultater, uanset hvor relevant eller veldesignet den er. Indeksering er et "
"grundlæggende skridt i :abbr:`SEO (søgemaskineoptimering)`, der fungerer som "
"grundlaget for en hjemmesides synlighed og organisk trafik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:147
msgid ""
"**When you first create your website on Odoo, it will not appear directly in "
"search engine results.** Search engines need time to crawl and index it, "
"which can take anywhere from a few days to several weeks. For Google, you "
"can use the :doc:`Search Console <../configuration/google_search_console>` "
"and request indexing for specific URLs, though this does not guarantee "
"faster results. If you have an existing website and are migrating, your "
"previous website may still appear instead of the new one during that "
"timeframe."
msgstr ""
"**Når du første gang opretter din hjemmeside på Odoo, vil den ikke vises "
"direkte i søgemaskiners resultater.** Søgemaskiner har brug for tid til at "
"crawle og indeksere den, hvilket kan tage alt fra nogle få dage til flere "
"uger. For Google kan du bruge :doc:`Search Console <../configuration/"
"google_search_console>` og anmode om indeksering af specifikke URL'er, "
"selvom dette ikke garanterer hurtigere resultater. Hvis du har en "
"eksisterende hjemmeside og migrerer, kan din tidligere hjemmeside stadig "
"vises i stedet for den nye i den tidsperiode."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:155
msgid "SEO impact when migrating your existing website to Odoo"
msgstr "SEO-påvirkning ved migrering af din eksisterende hjemmeside til Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:157
msgid ""
"In most cases, migrating to Odoo will not negatively impact the website's "
"SEO. While no platform can guarantee that rankings will remain unchanged, "
"follow these best practices to significantly reduce the risk."
msgstr ""
"I de fleste tilfælde vil migrering til Odoo ikke påvirke hjemmesidens SEO "
"negativt. Selvom ingen platform kan garantere, at placeringer forbliver "
"uændrede, skal du følge disse best practices for markant at reducere "
"risikoen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:161
msgid "Keep the existing content."
msgstr "Behold det eksisterende indhold."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:162
msgid ""
"Implement :ref:`redirects <website/pages/URL-redirection>` from old URLs to "
"their new counterparts."
msgstr ""
"Implementer :ref:`omdirigeringer <website/pages/URL-redirection>` fra gamle "
"URL'er til deres nye modstykker."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:164
msgid ""
"Monitor traffic and indexation to make sure that everything is going well, "
"using :doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`."
msgstr ""
"Overvåg trafik og indeksering for at sikre at alt forløber godt ved hjælp "
"af :doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:167
msgid ""
"By doing this, search engines reindex the site and maintain its visibility "
"in search results."
msgstr ""
"Ved at gøre dette genindekserer søgemaskiner webstedet og opretholder dets "
"synlighed i søgeresultater."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:170
msgid "It is normal to experience a traffic decrease in the first days."
msgstr "Det er normalt at opleve et fald i trafikken i de første dage."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:173
msgid "Prevent a page from being indexed"
msgstr "Forhindre en side i at blive indekseret"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:175
msgid ""
"To effectively prevent a page from appearing in search engine results, use "
"one of the following methods:"
msgstr ""
"For effektivt at forhindre en side i at vise sig i søgemaskiners resultater "
"skal du bruge en af følgende metoder:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:178
msgid ""
"**noindex tag:** Access the page's :ref:`properties <website/pages/"
"page_properties>` and toggle the :guilabel:`Indexed` switch off."
msgstr ""
"**noindex-tag:** Åbn sidens :ref:`egenskaber <website/pages/"
"page_properties>` og slå :guilabel:`Indekseret`-kontakten fra."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:182
msgid ""
"This option is not yet available for :ref:`dynamic pages <website/pages/"
"page_type>`."
msgstr ""
"Denne mulighed er endnu ikke tilgængelig for :ref:`dynamiske sider <website/"
"pages/page_type>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:184
msgid ""
"**404 or 403:** Configure the page to return a 404 (Not Found) or 403 "
"(Forbidden) HTTP status code. These codes signal to search engines that the "
"page does not exist or is inaccessible, leading to its eventual removal from "
"the index."
msgstr ""
"**404 eller 403:** Konfigurer siden til at returnere en 404 (Ikke fundet) "
"eller 403 (Forbudt) HTTP-statuskode. Disse koder signalerer til "
"søgemaskiner, at siden ikke eksisterer eller er utilgængelig, hvilket fører "
"til dens eventuelle fjernelse fra indekset."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:188
msgid ""
"**404:** :ref:`Configure a 404 redirection. <website/pages/URL-redirection>`"
msgstr ""
"**404:** :ref:`Konfigurer en 404-omdirigering. <website/pages/URL-"
"redirection>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:189
msgid ""
"**403:** Access the page's :ref:`properties <website/pages/page_properties>` "
"and toggle the :guilabel:`Visibility` switch off or :ref:`unpublish the page "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`."
msgstr ""
"**403:** Åbn sidens :ref:`egenskaber <website/pages/page_properties>` og "
"slå :guilabel:`Synlighed`-kontakten fra eller :ref:`afpublicer siden "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:193
msgid ""
"**Google Search Console:** Use Google Search Console to request the removal "
"of specific URLs from Google's index."
msgstr ""
"**Google Search Console:** Brug Google Search Console til at anmode om "
"fjernelse af specifikke URL'er fra Googles indeks."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:197
msgid ":doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`"
msgstr ":doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:198
msgid ":doc:`pages`"
msgstr ":doc:`pages`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:201
msgid "Prevent a website from being indexed"
msgstr "Forhindre en hjemmeside i at blive indekseret"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:203
msgid ""
"To prevent a website from appearing in search engine results, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`, then in "
"the :guilabel:`Website Info` section, add a random value in "
"the :guilabel:`Domain` field. Doing so automatically inserts the following "
"tag into the page source:"
msgstr ""
"For at forhindre en hjemmeside i at vises i søgemaskiners resultater, gå "
"til :menuselection:`Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og tilføj derefter en "
"tilfældig værdi i feltet :guilabel:`Domæne` i "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Hjemmeside-info`. Ved at gøre dette indsættes "
"automatisk følgende tag i sidens kildekode:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:212
msgid ""
"This tag instructs search engines not to index the site. After applying the "
"change, it may take several days or weeks for search engines to update their "
"results and remove the website."
msgstr ""
"Dette tag instruerer søgemaskiner om ikke at indeksere sitet. Efter "
"anvendelse af ændringen kan det tage flere dage eller uger før søgemaskiner "
"opdaterer deres resultater og fjerner hjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:216
msgid ""
"This can be used to prevent websites from test databases from appearing in "
"search results."
msgstr ""
"Dette kan bruges til at forhindre hjemmesider fra testdatabaser i at vises i "
"søgeresultater."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:219
msgid "Sitemap"
msgstr "Sitemap"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:221
msgid ""
"The sitemap points out website pages and their relation to each other to "
"search engine crawlers. Odoo generates a `/sitemap.xml` file, including all "
"URLs. For performance reasons, this file is cached and updated every 12 "
"hours."
msgstr ""
"Sitemap'et påpeger hjemmesidens sider og deres relation til hinanden for "
"søgemaskinecrawlere. Odoo genererer en `/sitemap.xml`-fil, der inkluderer "
"alle URL'er. Af performancehensyn caches denne fil og opdateres hver 12. "
"time."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:226
msgid ""
"If your website has a lot of pages, Odoo automatically creates a Sitemap "
"Index file, respecting the `sitemaps.org protocol <http://www.sitemaps.org/"
"protocol.html>`_, grouping sitemap URLs in 45000 chunks per file."
msgstr ""
"Hvis dit websted har mange sider, opretter Odoo automatisk en Sitemap Index-"
"fil, der respekterer `sitemaps.org-protokollen <http://www.sitemaps.org/"
"protocol.html>`_, og grupperer sitemap-URL'er i bidder på 45000 pr. fil."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:230
msgid ""
"Every sitemap entry has three attributes that are computed automatically:"
msgstr "Hver sitemap-post har tre attributter, der beregnes automatisk:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:232
msgid "`<loc>`: the URL of a page."
msgstr "`<loc>`: URL'en på en side."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:233
msgid ""
"`<lastmod>`: last modification date of the resource, computed automatically "
"based on the related object. For a page related to a product, this could be "
"the last modification date of the product or the page."
msgstr ""
"`<lastmod>`: sidste ændringsdato for ressourcen, beregnet automatisk baseret "
"på det relaterede objekt. For en side relateret til et produkt kan dette "
"være den sidste ændringsdato for produktet eller siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:236
msgid ""
"`<priority>`: modules may implement their priority algorithm based on their "
"content (for example, a forum might assign a priority based on the number of "
"votes on a specific post). The priority of a static page is defined by its "
"priority field, which is normalized (16 is the default)."
msgstr ""
"`<priority>`: moduler kan implementere deres prioritetsalgoritme baseret på "
"deres indhold (f.eks. kan et forum tildele en prioritet baseret på antallet "
"af stemmer på et bestemt indlæg). Prioriteten af en statisk side er "
"defineret af dens prioritetsfelt, som er normaliseret (16 er standarden)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:241
msgid ""
"To prevent pages from appearing in a sitemap, go to :menuselection:`Site --> "
"Properties`, and toggle off the :guilabel:`Indexed` feature."
msgstr ""
"For at forhindre sider i at vises i et sitemap, gå til :menuselection:`Site "
"--> Egenskaber`, og slå funktionen :guilabel:`Indekseret` fra."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:0
msgid "toggle off the “Indexed” field"
msgstr "slå feltet “Indekseret” fra"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:248
msgid "robots.txt"
msgstr "robots.txt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:250
msgid ""
"A `robots.txt` file instructs search engine crawlers which parts of a "
"website they are permitted to access. Its primary purpose is to:"
msgstr ""
"En `robots.txt`-fil instruerer søgemaskinecrawlere om, hvilke dele af en "
"hjemmeside de har tilladelse til at få adgang til. Dens primære formål er at:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:253
msgid ""
"**Prevent overloading the website:** By guiding crawlers away from certain "
"sections, robots.txt helps manage server load."
msgstr ""
"**Forhindre overbelastning af hjemmesiden:** Ved at guide crawlere væk fra "
"visse sektioner hjælper robots.txt med at styre serverbelastningen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:255
msgid ""
"**Control access to resources and detailed descriptions:** It can prevent "
"crawlers from accessing media files (images, videos), CSS stylesheets, and "
"JavaScript files, and from reading the content (text) of specific pages."
msgstr ""
"**Kontrollere adgang til ressourcer og detaljerede beskrivelser:** Den kan "
"forhindre crawlere i at få adgang til mediefiler (billeder, videoer), CSS-"
"stylesheets og JavaScript-filer og i at læse indholdet (tekst) på specifikke "
"sider."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:259
msgid ""
"When indexing your website, search engines first look at the robots.txt "
"file. Odoo automatically creates one robot.txt file available on "
"`mydatabase.odoo.com/robots.txt`."
msgstr ""
"Når søgemaskiner indekserer din hjemmeside, kigger de først på robots.txt-"
"filen. Odoo opretter automatisk én robots.txt-fil tilgængelig på "
"`midatabase.odoo.com/robots.txt`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:263
msgid ""
"Reputable bots adhere to robots.txt; others may require blocking "
"via :ref:`Cloudflare <domain-name/existing/naked/cloudflare>` on your custom "
"domain."
msgstr ""
"Velrenommerede bots overholder robots.txt; andre kan kræve blokering "
"via :ref:`Cloudflare <domain-name/existing/naked/cloudflare>` på dit "
"brugerdefinerede domæne."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:267
msgid "Edit robots.txt"
msgstr "Redigér robots.txt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:269
msgid ""
"By editing a robots.txt file, you can control which site pages are "
"accessible to search engine crawlers. To add custom instructions to the "
"file, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll "
"down to the :guilabel:`SEO` section, and click :guilabel:`Edit robots.txt`."
msgstr ""
"Ved at redigere en robots.txt-fil kan du kontrollere, hvilke websider der er "
"tilgængelige for søgemaskinecrawlere. For at tilføje brugerdefinerede "
"instruktioner til filen skal du gå til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> "
"Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, scrolle ned til sektionen :guilabel:`SEO` "
"og klikke på :guilabel:`Rediger robots.txt`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:274
msgid ""
"If you do not want robots to crawl the `/about-us` page of your site, you "
"can edit the robots.txt file to add `Disallow: /about-us`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ikke ønsker, at robotter skal crawle `/about-us`-siden på dit "
"websted, kan du redigere robots.txt-filen for at tilføje `Disallow: /about-"
"us`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:278
msgid ""
"While `robots.txt` prevents content from being crawled, **it does not "
"guarantee that a page will not be indexed**. A page can still appear in "
"search results if it is linked to from other crawled pages (indexed by "
"\"reference\"). Google generally does not recommend using robots.txt to "
"block webpages that you wish to keep out of search results entirely."
msgstr ""
"Selvom `robots.txt` forhindrer indhold i at blive crawlet, **garanterer det "
"ikke, at en side ikke vil blive indekseret**. En side kan stadig vises i "
"søgeresultater, hvis der linkes til den fra andre crawlede sider (indekseret "
"ved \"reference\"). Google anbefaler generelt ikke at bruge robots.txt til "
"at blokere websider, som du ønsker at holde helt ude af søgeresultater."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:284
msgid "Advanced features"
msgstr "Avancerede funktioner"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:287
msgid "Structured data markup"
msgstr "Struktureret data-markup"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:289
msgid ""
"Structured data markup is used to generate rich snippets in search engine "
"results. It is a way for websites to send structured data to search engine "
"crawlers, helping them understand your content and create well-presented "
"search results."
msgstr ""
"Struktureret data-opmærkning bruges til at generere rige uddrag i "
"søgemaskiners resultater. Det er en måde for hjemmesider at sende "
"strukturerede data til søgemaskinecrawlere, der hjælper dem med at forstå "
"dit indhold og skabe velpræsenterede søgeresultater."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:293
msgid ""
"By default, Google supports many `rich snippets <https://"
"developers.google.com/search/blog/2009/05/introducing-rich-snippets>`_ for "
"content types, including Reviews, People, Products, Businesses, Events, and "
"Organizations."
msgstr ""
"Som standard understøtter Google mange `rich snippets <https://"
"developers.google.com/search/blog/2009/05/introducing-rich-snippets>`_ for "
"indholdstyper, herunder anmeldelser, personer, produkter, virksomheder, "
"arrangementer og organisationer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:296
msgid ""
"Microdata is a set of tags, introduced with HTML5, that help search engines "
"better understand your content and display it in a relevant way. Odoo "
"implements microdata as defined in the schema.org `specification <https://"
"schema.org/docs/gs.html>`_ for events, eCommerce products, forum posts, and "
"contact addresses. This allows your product pages to be displayed in Google "
"using extra information like the price and rating of a product:"
msgstr ""
"Microdata er et sæt tags, introduceret med HTML5, der hjælper søgemaskiner "
"med bedre at forstå dit indhold og vise det på en relevant måde. Odoo "
"implementerer microdata som defineret i schema.org-`specifikationen <https://"
"schema.org/docs/gs.html>`_ for arrangementer, webshop-produkter, forumindlæg "
"og kontaktadresser. Dette gør det muligt for dine produktsider at blive vist "
"i Google med ekstra information såsom pris og vurdering af et produkt:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:None
msgid "snippets in search engine results"
msgstr "snippets i søgemaskiners resultater"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:306
msgid "Hreflang HTML tags"
msgstr "Hreflang HTML-tags"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:308
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically includes `hreflang` and `x-default` tags in the code of "
"your website's multilingual pages. These HTML attributes are crucial in "
"informing search engines about a specific page's language and geographical "
"targeting."
msgstr ""
"Odoo inkluderer automatisk `hreflang`- og `x-default`-tags i koden på dit "
"websteds flersprogede sider. Disse HTML-attributter er afgørende for at "
"informere søgemaskiner om en bestemt sides sprog og geografiske målretning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:313
msgid ":doc:`../configuration/translate`"
msgstr ":doc:`../configuration/translate`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:9
msgid ""
"Design your website using :doc:`building blocks <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>`, customize its :doc:`theme <../website/web_design/themes>` "
"with various options, structure and present content with :doc:`elements <../"
"website/web_design/elements>`, and display or hide building blocks "
"using :doc:`visibility settings <../website/web_design/visibility>`."
msgstr ""
"Design din hjemmeside ved hjælp af :doc:`byggeklodser <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>`, tilpas dens :doc:`tema <../website/web_design/themes>` "
"med forskellige muligheder, strukturer og præsenter indhold "
"med :doc:`elementer <../website/web_design/elements>`, og vis eller skjul "
"byggeklodser ved hjælp af :doc:`indstillinger for synlighed <../website/"
"web_design/visibility>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:16
msgid ""
"Design your website by dragging and dropping building blocks, then editing "
"them to fit your content and layout needs."
msgstr ""
"Design din hjemmeside ved at trække og slippe byggeklodser og derefter "
"redigere dem, så de passer til dit indhold og layout."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:23
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:3
msgid "General theme"
msgstr "Generelt tema"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:23
msgid ""
"Customize your website’s theme by adjusting its colors, fonts, and layout."
msgstr ""
"Tilpas din hjemmesides tema ved at justere farver, skrifttyper og layout."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:29
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:3
msgid "Elements"
msgstr "Elementer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:29
msgid ""
"Structure and present content effectively with elements such as titles, "
"lists, etc."
msgstr ""
"Strukturer og præsenter indhold effektivt med elementer som titler, lister "
"osv."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:35
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:3
msgid "Visibility"
msgstr "Overblik"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:35
msgid "Display or hide building blocks based on several criteria."
msgstr "Vis eller skjul byggeklodser baseret på flere kriterier."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:7
msgid ""
"You can design your website by :ref:`dragging and dropping building blocks "
"<website/building_blocks/add>`, then :ref:`editing them <website/"
"building_blocks/edit>` to fit your content and layout needs."
msgstr ""
"Du kan designe din hjemmeside ved at :ref:`trække og slippe byggeklodser "
"<website/building_blocks/add>`, og derefter :ref:`redigere dem <website/"
"building_blocks/edit>` så de passer til dit indhold og layoutbehov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:12
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorial: Design your website: text and colors <https://www.odoo.com/"
"slides/slide/design-your-website-text-and-colors-6930?fullscreen=1>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Tutorial: Design din hjemmeside: tekst og farver <https://www.odoo.com/"
"slides/slide/design-your-website-text-and-colors-6930?fullscreen=1>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:17
msgid "Add a building block"
msgstr "Tilføje en byggeklods"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:19
msgid ""
"To add a block to a :doc:`website page <../structure/pages>`, access the "
"page, click :guilabel:`Edit`, then drag and drop the desired building block "
"into the appropriate location. Two types of building blocks are "
"available: :guilabel:`Categories` and :guilabel:`Inner "
"Content`. :guilabel:`Inner Content` building blocks can only be added "
"into :guilabel:`Categories` building blocks."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en blok til en :doc:`hjemmesideside <../structure/pages>`, "
"skal du gå til siden, klikke på :guilabel:`Rediger`, og derefter trække og "
"slippe den ønskede byggeklods på det passende sted. To typer byggeklodser er "
"tilgængelige: :guilabel:`Kategorier` og :guilabel:`Indre "
"indhold`. :guilabel:`Indre indhold` byggeklodser kan kun tilføjes "
"i :guilabel:`Kategorier` byggeklodser."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:25
msgid ""
"When clicking a category block, a popup appears, allowing you to select "
"between multiple templates for each category."
msgstr ""
"Når du klikker på en kategoriblok, vises en popup, der giver dig mulighed "
"for at vælge mellem flere skabeloner for hver kategori."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:29
msgid ""
"Search for a specific block in the :guilabel:`Insert a block` popup using "
"the search bar."
msgstr ""
"Søg efter en specifik blok i :guilabel:`Indsæt en blok`-popup'en ved hjælp "
"af søgefeltet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Pop-up block selection"
msgstr "Pop-up blokvalg"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:34
msgid ""
"Once the category block is placed, you can drag and drop :guilabel:`Inner "
"content` blocks within it. The :guilabel:`Inner content` blocks allow you to "
"add elements, such as videos, images, social media buttons, etc., into pre-"
"existing category blocks."
msgstr ""
"Når kategoriblokken er placeret, kan du trække og slippe :guilabel:`Indre "
"indhold` blokke inden i den. :guilabel:`Indre indhold` blokkene giver dig "
"mulighed for at tilføje elementer, såsom videoer, billeder, sociale "
"medieknapper osv., til allerede eksisterende kategoriblokke."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:39
msgid ""
"You can also add a building block on the login page. To do so, navigate to "
"the website's homepage, add `/web/login` to the URL and press `Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan også tilføje en byggeblok på login-siden. For at gøre dette skal du "
"navigere til hjemmesidens startside, tilføje `/web/login` til URL'en og "
"trykke på `Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:41
msgid ""
"Access to certain blocks requires installing their respective application or "
"module (e.g., eCommerce for the :guilabel:`Products` block)."
msgstr ""
"Adgang til visse blokke kræver installation af deres respektive applikation "
"eller modul (f.eks. Webshop for :guilabel:`Produkter`-blokken)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:45
msgid ""
"Add all your social media accounts in one place with the inner "
"content :guilabel:`Social Media` block. Toggle the switch on or off next to "
"the desired platform and copy/paste your account URL."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj alle dine sociale mediekonti ét sted med det indre "
"indhold :guilabel:`Sociale medier` blok. Slå kontakten til eller fra ved "
"siden af den ønskede platform og kopier/indsæt din konto-URL."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Social Media inner content block"
msgstr "Sociale medier indre indholdblok"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:54
msgid "Form"
msgstr "Formular"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:56
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Form` block is used to collect information from website "
"visitors and, if applicable, create records in your database. To add a form "
"to a website page, drag and drop the :guilabel:`Contact & Forms` category "
"block, then select a block in the popup."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Formular`-blokken bruges til at indsamle oplysninger fra "
"hjemmesidebesøgende og, hvis relevant, oprette poster i din database. For at "
"tilføje en formular til en hjemmesideside skal du trække og "
"slippe :guilabel:`Kontakt & Formularer`-kategoriblokken og derefter vælge en "
"blok i popup'en."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:None
msgid "Example of a form block"
msgstr "Eksempel på en formularblok"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:66
msgid "Action"
msgstr "Handling"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:68
msgid ""
"By default, when the form is submitted, an email containing the information "
"entered by the visitor is automatically sent. Depending on the apps "
"installed on your database, additional actions that can automatically create "
"records may become available. To choose a different action, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit`, click the form, navigate to the :guilabel:`Style` "
"tab, and select the desired :guilabel:`Action`:"
msgstr ""
"Som standard sendes der automatisk en e-mail med de oplysninger, som den "
"besøgende har indtastet, når formularen indsendes. Afhængigt af de apps, der "
"er installeret på din database, kan der blive tilgængelige yderligere "
"handlinger, som automatisk kan oprette poster. For at vælge en anden "
"handling skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Rediger`, klikke på formularen, "
"navigere til fanen :guilabel:`Stil` og vælge den "
"ønskede :guilabel:`Handling`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Apply for a Job` (:doc:`Recruitment </applications/hr/"
"recruitment>`)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ansøg om et job` (:doc:`Ansættelse </applications/hr/"
"recruitment>`)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:75
msgid ":guilabel:`Create a Customer` (:doc:`eCommerce <../../ecommerce>`)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Opret en kunde` (:doc:`Webshop <../../ecommerce>`)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Create a Ticket` (:doc:`Helpdesk </applications/services/"
"helpdesk>`)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opret en sag` (:doc:`Kundeservice </applications/services/"
"helpdesk>`)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:77
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Create an Opportunity` (:doc:`CRM </applications/sales/crm>`)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Opret en mulighed` (:doc:`CRM </applications/sales/crm>`)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Subscribe to Newsletter` (:doc:`Email Marketing </applications/"
"marketing/email_marketing>`)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Abonner på nyhedsbrev` (:doc:`E-mailmarketing </applications/"
"marketing/email_marketing>`)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Create a Task` (:doc:`Project </applications/services/project>`)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opret en opgave` (:doc:`Projekt </applications/services/project>`)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:80
msgid ":guilabel:`More models`: to generate other types of records"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Flere modeller`: til at generere andre typer af poster"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:82
msgid ""
"By default, submitting the form redirects visitors to a *Thank you* page. "
"Use the :guilabel:`URL` field to send them to a different page. "
"Alternatively, you can choose not to redirect and keep them on the form's "
"page by selecting :guilabel:`Nothing` or :guilabel:`Show Message` in "
"the :guilabel:`On Success` field."
msgstr ""
"Som standard omdirigerer indsendelse af formularen besøgende til en *Tak* "
"side. Brug feltet :guilabel:`URL` til at sende dem til en anden side. "
"Alternativt kan du vælge ikke at omdirigere og beholde dem på formularens "
"side ved at vælge :guilabel:`Intet` eller :guilabel:`Vis besked` i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Ved succes`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:90
msgid "Fields"
msgstr "Felter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:92
msgid ""
"To add a new field to the form, navigate to the :guilabel:`Style` tab and "
"click the :guilabel:`+ Field` button next to the :guilabel:`Form` "
"or :guilabel:`Field` section. To modify any field on the form, select the "
"field, then use the options available in the :guilabel:`Field` section of "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab. For example, you can:"
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje et nyt felt til formularen skal du navigere til "
"fanen :guilabel:`Stil` og klikke på knappen :guilabel:`+ Felt` ved siden af "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Formular` eller :guilabel:`Felt`. For at ændre et felt "
"på formularen skal du vælge feltet og derefter bruge de tilgængelige "
"indstillinger i sektionen :guilabel:`Felt` på fanen :guilabel:`Stil`. Du kan "
"f.eks.:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:97
msgid "Change the field :guilabel:`Type`."
msgstr "Skift feltets :guilabel:`Type`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:100
msgid ""
"It is also possible to select an :guilabel:`Existing Field` from the "
"database and use the data it contains. The fields available depend on the "
"selected action. Property fields added to the database can also be used."
msgstr ""
"Det er også muligt at vælge et :guilabel:`Eksisterende felt` fra databasen "
"og bruge de data, det indeholder. De tilgængelige felter afhænger af den "
"valgte handling. Egenskabsfelter, der er tilføjet til databasen, kan også "
"bruges."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "All types of form fields"
msgstr "Alle typer formularfelter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:109
msgid ""
"Some fields are visually similar, but the data entered must follow a "
"specific format."
msgstr ""
"Nogle felter ligner hinanden visuelt, men de indtastede data skal følge et "
"specifikt format."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:111
msgid "Edit the field's :guilabel:`Label` and adapt its :guilabel:`Position`."
msgstr ""
"Rediger feltets :guilabel:`etiket` og tilpas dets :guilabel:`position`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:112
msgid ""
"Enable a field :guilabel:`Description`. Toggle the switch on and click the "
"default description on the form to modify it."
msgstr ""
"Aktivér en felt-:guilabel:`Beskrivelse`. Slå kontakten til, og klik på "
"standardbeskrivelsen på formularen for at ændre den."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:114
msgid "Add a :guilabel:`Placeholder` or :guilabel:`Default value`."
msgstr "Tilføj en :guilabel:`pladsholder` eller :guilabel:`standardværdi`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:115
msgid "Specify if the field is :guilabel:`Required`."
msgstr "Angiv om feltet er :guilabel:`påkrævet`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:116
msgid "Edit the field's :doc:`visibility <visibility>` settings."
msgstr "Rediger feltets :doc:`synlighedsindstillinger <visibility>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:117
msgid "Add an :ref:`animation <website/elements/animations>`."
msgstr "Tilføj en :ref:`animation <website/elements/animations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:119
msgid "Once you have made the desired changes, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Når du har foretaget de ønskede ændringer, klik på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:122
msgid "Add an Odoo contact form on a non-Odoo website"
msgstr "Tilføj en Odoo-kontaktformular på en ikke-Odoo-hjemmeside"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:124
msgid ""
"You can display an Odoo contact form on another website using an iframe. To "
"do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Du kan vise en Odoo-kontaktformular på en anden hjemmeside ved hjælp af en "
"iframe. For at gøre dette, følg disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:127
msgid ""
"**Prepare the Odoo form:** Create a contact form on a page in Odoo Website "
"and remove the :ref:`header design <website/header_footer/header-design>` "
"and the :ref:`footer design <website/header_footer/footer-design>`. Make "
"sure only the contact form remains on the page."
msgstr ""
"**Forbered Odoo-formularen:** Opret en kontaktformular på en side i Odoo "
"Hjemmeside og fjern :ref:`header-designet <website/header_footer/header-"
"design>` og :ref:`footer-designet <website/header_footer/footer-design>`. "
"Sørg for at kun kontaktformularen forbliver på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:130
msgid ""
"**Generate an embeddable code:** Copy the URL of the Odoo form page and "
"paste it into an iframe generator, such as `La Digitale.dev <https://"
"ladigitale.dev/digitools/generateur-iframe>`_ or `iFrame Generator <https://"
"www.iframe-generator.com/>`_ . Adjust the width and height for proper "
"display."
msgstr ""
"**Generér en indlejrbar kode:** Kopiér URL'en til Odoo-formularsiden og "
"indsæt den i en iframe-generator, såsom `La Digitale.dev <https://"
"ladigitale.dev/digitools/generateur-iframe>`_ eller `iFrame Generator "
"<https://www.iframe-generator.com/>`_. Justér bredde og højde for korrekt "
"visning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:134
msgid ""
"**Add the embedded code to the non-Odoo website:** Open the relevant page’s "
"HTML (in the code editor or CMS) and insert the embedded code where the form "
"should be displayed."
msgstr ""
"**Tilføj den indlejrede kode til den ikke-Odoo-hjemmeside:** Åbn den "
"relevante sides HTML (i kodeeditoren eller CMS'et) og indsæt den indlejrede "
"kode, hvor formularen skal vises."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:138
msgid "Example of an embedded code:"
msgstr "Eksempel på en indlejret kode:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:157
msgid "Embed code"
msgstr "Integrér kode"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:159
msgid ""
"Embedding code allows you to integrate content from third-party services "
"into a page, such as videos from YouTube, maps from Google Maps, social "
"media posts from Instagram, etc."
msgstr ""
"Indlejret kode giver dig mulighed for at integrere indhold fra "
"tredjepartstjenester på en side, såsom videoer fra YouTube, kort fra Google "
"Maps, opslag på sociale medier fra Instagram osv."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:162
msgid ""
"After dragging and dropping the :guilabel:`Embed Code` block from "
"the :guilabel:`Inner Content` section into a page, click the block, then go "
"to the :guilabel:`Style` tab and click :guilabel:`Edit`. Replace the "
"placeholder code with your custom embed code."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have trukket og sluppet :guilabel:`Indlejret kode`-blokken fra "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Indre indhold` ind på en side skal du klikke på "
"blokken, derefter gå til fanen :guilabel:`Stil` og klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Rediger`. Erstat pladsholderkoden med din brugerdefinerede "
"indlejrede kode."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:None
msgid "Add the link to the embedded code you want to point to"
msgstr "Tilføj linket til den indlejrede kode, du vil pege på"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:170
msgid ""
"Do not copy/paste code you do not understand, as it could put your data at "
"risk."
msgstr ""
"Kopier/indsæt ikke kode, du ikke forstår, da det kan bringe dine data i fare."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:175
msgid "Move, switch, duplicate or delete a building block"
msgstr "Flyt, skift, dupliker eller slet en byggeblok"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:177
msgid ""
"Pull the turquoise borders on the block to reduce or increase the space at "
"the top or bottom of it."
msgstr ""
"Træk i de turkisblå kanter på blokken for at reducere eller øge mellemrummet "
"i toppen eller bunden af den."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:179
msgid ""
"Change the block order by clicking :icon:`fa-chevron-up` (:guilabel:`chevron "
"up`) or :icon:`fa-chevron-down` (:guilabel:`chevron down`) and move the "
"block on the page by clicking :icon:`fa-arrows` (:guilabel:`arrows`). When "
"you have multiple :ref:`columns <website/building_blocks/cols>`, move a "
"column to the left or right by clicking :icon:`fa-chevron-left` "
"(:guilabel:`chevron left`) or :icon:`fa-chevron-right` (:guilabel:`chevron "
"right`)."
msgstr ""
"Skift blokrækkefølgen ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-chevron-up` "
"(:guilabel:`chevron op`) eller :icon:`fa-chevron-down` (:guilabel:`chevron "
"ned`) og flyt blokken på siden ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-arrows` "
"(:guilabel:`pile`). Når du har flere :ref:`kolonner <website/building_blocks/"
"cols>`, flyt en kolonne til venstre eller højre ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-"
"chevron-left` (:guilabel:`chevron venstre`) eller :icon:`fa-chevron-right` "
"(:guilabel:`chevron højre`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:186
msgid ""
"To duplicate a building block, click :icon:`fa-clone` "
"(:guilabel:`duplicate`). Once duplicated, the new block appears on the page "
"beneath the original one."
msgstr ""
"For at duplikere en byggeblok skal du klikke på :icon:`fa-clone` "
"(:guilabel:`dupliker`). Når den er duplikeret, vises den nye blok på siden "
"under den originale."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:190
msgid ""
"Alternatively, click the :icon:`fa-clone` (:guilabel:`duplicate`) icon at "
"the top of the :guilabel:`Style` tab to duplicate the selected block."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-clone` (:guilabel:`dupliker`) "
"øverst på fanen :guilabel:`Stil` for at duplikere den valgte blok."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:193
msgid "To delete a block, click :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`trash`)."
msgstr ""
"For at slette en blok skal du klikke på :icon:`fa-trash` "
"(:guilabel:`papirkurv`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Extend margins on building block"
msgstr "Udvid margener på byggeblok"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:201
msgid "Edit a building block"
msgstr "Rediger en byggeblok"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:203
msgid ""
"To edit the content of a building block, click it and go to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab. Available customization options vary depending on "
"the type of block selected."
msgstr ""
"For at redigere indholdet af en byggeblok skal du klikke på den og gå til "
"fanen :guilabel:`Stil`. Tilgængelige tilpasningsmuligheder varierer "
"afhængigt af den type blok, der er valgt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:207
msgid ":doc:`Web design elements <elements>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Webdesignelementer <elements>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:208
msgid ":doc:`Visibility <visibility>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Synlighed <visibility>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:211
msgid "Background"
msgstr "Baggrund"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:213
msgid ""
"To modify the background of a building block, select the block, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and click the color dot or "
"another :guilabel:`Background` option. You can change the color and/or add "
"an image, video, and/or shape. Once you've selected a shape, new fields "
"appear to allow you to customize the shape."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre baggrunden på en byggeblok skal du vælge blokken, gå til "
"fanen :guilabel:`Stil` og klikke på farveprikken eller en "
"anden :guilabel:`Baggrund`-indstilling. Du kan ændre farven og/eller tilføje "
"et billede, en video og/eller en form. Når du har valgt en form, vises nye "
"felter, så du kan tilpasse formen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:219
msgid ""
"Position an element (image, text, etc.) behind or in front of another one by "
"using the :guilabel:`Send to back` or :guilabel:`Bring to front` icons."
msgstr ""
"Placer et element (billede, tekst osv.) bag eller foran et andet ved at "
"bruge ikonerne :guilabel:`Send bagerst` eller :guilabel:`Bring forrest`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Change block position"
msgstr "Skift blokposition"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:225
msgid ""
"To resize a block, click and drag the dots around its edges to adjust it as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre størrelsen på en blok skal du klikke og trække i prikkerne "
"omkring dens kanter for at justere den efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:0
msgid "Adapt block size"
msgstr "Tilpas blokstørrelse"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:231
msgid ":doc:`General theme <themes>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Generelt tema <themes>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:234
msgid "Layout: grid and columns"
msgstr "Layout: gitter og kolonner"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:236
msgid ""
"For most building blocks, you can choose between two layout "
"styles: :ref:`grid <website/building_blocks/grid>` or :ref:`columns (cols) "
"<website/building_blocks/cols>`. To change the default layout style, click "
"the block, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and set the :guilabel:`Layout` "
"field to :guilabel:`Grid` or :guilabel:`Cols`."
msgstr ""
"For de fleste byggeblokke kan du vælge mellem to layoutstile: :ref:`gitter "
"<website/building_blocks/grid>` eller :ref:`kolonner (cols) <website/"
"building_blocks/cols>`. For at ændre standardlayoutstilen skal du klikke på "
"blokken, gå til fanen :guilabel:`Stil` og indstille "
"feltet :guilabel:`Layout` til :guilabel:`Gitter` eller :guilabel:`Cols`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:244
msgid "Grid"
msgstr "Gitter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:246
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Grid` layout allows you to reposition and resize elements, "
"such as images or text, by dragging and dropping them. When :guilabel:`Grid` "
"is selected, additional options are available to :guilabel:`Add Elements` by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Image`, :guilabel:`Text`, or :guilabel:`Button`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gitter`-layoutet giver dig mulighed for at flytte og tilpasse "
"størrelsen på elementer, såsom billeder eller tekst, ved at trække og slippe "
"dem. Når :guilabel:`Gitter` er valgt, er der yderligere muligheder "
"tilgængelige for at :guilabel:`tilføje elementer` ved at klikke "
"på :guilabel:`billede`, :guilabel:`tekst` eller :guilabel:`knap`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:None
msgid ""
"When the grid layout is selected, choose an image and drag and drop it where "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Når gitterlayoutet er valgt, skal du vælge et billede og trække og slippe "
"det, hvor det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:256
msgid "Cols"
msgstr "Spalter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:258
msgid ""
"Choosing the :guilabel:`Cols` layout allows you to determine the number of "
"elements per line within the block. To do so, select the block to modify, "
"click the dropdown next to the :guilabel:`Cols` field, and adjust the "
"number. You can then modify a specific column's settings using the options "
"in the :guilabel:`Column` section of the :guilabel:`Style` tab."
msgstr ""
"Valg af layoutet :guilabel:`Cols` giver dig mulighed for at bestemme "
"antallet af elementer pr. linje inden for blokken. For at gøre dette skal du "
"vælge den blok, der skal ændres, klikke på rullemenuen ved siden af "
"feltet :guilabel:`Cols` og justere antallet. Du kan derefter ændre en "
"specifik kolonnes indstillinger ved hjælp af mulighederne i "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Column` under fanen :guilabel:`Style`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:264
msgid ""
"By default, :doc:`on mobile devices <visibility>`, only one element (column) "
"is visible per line to ensure that content remains easily readable and "
"accessible on smaller screens. To adjust the value, click the :icon:`fa-"
"mobile` (:guilabel:`mobile icon`) at the top of the website editor and adapt "
"the number of columns. Shapes are hidden by default on mobiles."
msgstr ""
"Som standard er :doc:`på mobile enheder <visibility>` kun ét element "
"(kolonne) synligt pr. linje for at sikre, at indholdet forbliver let "
"læseligt og tilgængeligt på mindre skærme. For at justere værdien skal du "
"klikke på :icon:`fa-mobile` (:guilabel:`mobilikonet`) øverst i "
"hjemmesideeditoren og tilpasse antallet af kolonner. Former er skjult som "
"standard på mobile enheder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:272
msgid "Save a custom building block"
msgstr "Gem en tilpasset byggeblok"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:274
msgid ""
"You can save a customized building block to reuse it elsewhere. To do so, "
"select it, navigate to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and click the :icon:`fa-"
"floppy-o` (:guilabel:`floppy disk`) icon. Click the :guilabel:`Save` button "
"in the popup to confirm saving your custom block."
msgstr ""
"Du kan gemme en tilpasset byggesten for at genbruge den andre steder. For at "
"gøre dette skal du vælge den, navigere til fanen :guilabel:`Style` og klikke "
"på ikonet :icon:`fa-floppy-o` (:guilabel:`diskette`). Klik på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Save` i pop op-vinduet for at bekræfte, at du gemmer din "
"tilpassede blok."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:278
msgid ""
"To add a saved building block to the page, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Blocks` tab and drag and drop the :guilabel:`Custom` block "
"from the :guilabel:`Categories` section. In the popup that opens, click the "
"desired block in the :guilabel:`Custom` category."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en gemt byggeblok til siden skal du navigere til "
"fanen :guilabel:`blokke` og trække og slippe :guilabel:`tilpasset`-blokken "
"fra sektionen :guilabel:`kategorier`. I pop op-vinduet, der åbnes, skal du "
"klikke på den ønskede blok i kategorien :guilabel:`tilpasset`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:283
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Insert a block` popup, click :icon:`fa-pencil` "
"(:guilabel:`edit`) to rename the custom block or :icon:`fa-trash` "
"(:guilabel:`delete`) to delete it."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`indsæt en blok` skal du klikke på :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` (:guilabel:`rediger`) for at omdøbe den tilpassede blok "
"eller :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`slet`) for at slette den."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:289
msgid "Create an anchor link"
msgstr "Opret et ankerlink"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:291
msgid ""
"Anchor links are hyperlinks that direct users to a **specific section** of a "
"page. To create an anchor link for a block, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Ankerlinks er hyperlinks, der dirigerer brugere til et **specifikt afsnit** "
"på en side. For at oprette et ankerlink til en blok skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:294
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Edit` and select the block you want to link to."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`rediger`, og vælg den blok, du vil linke til."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:295
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-link` (:guilabel:`link`) at the top of the :guilabel:`Style` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-link` (:guilabel:`link`) øverst i fanen :guilabel:`Style`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:296
msgid ""
"To edit the default anchor name, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the green popup "
"message that opens."
msgstr ""
"For at redigere standardankernavnet skal du klikke på :guilabel:`rediger` i "
"den grønne pop op-meddelelse, der åbnes."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:297
msgid "Replace the anchor name and click :guilabel:`Save & copy`."
msgstr "Erstat ankernavnet, og klik på :guilabel:`gem og kopier`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:299
msgid ""
"Once the anchor is saved, you can :ref:`link to it <website/elements/links>` "
"from anywhere on your website."
msgstr ""
"Når ankeret er gemt, kan du :ref:`linke til det <website/elements/links>` "
"fra hvor som helst på din hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:5
msgid ""
"Elements help structure and present content effectively. They range from "
"text-based components like :ref:`titles <website/elements/"
"titles>`, :ref:`lists <website/elements/lists>` and :ref:`text highlights "
"<website/elements/text_highlights>` to interactive ones such "
"as :ref:`buttons <website/elements/buttons>` and :ref:`links <website/"
"elements/links>`. Visual elements like :ref:`images <website/elements/"
"images>`, :ref:`icons <website/elements/icons>`, :ref:`videos <website/"
"elements/videos>`, and :ref:`animations <website/elements/animations>` can "
"also be added to improve content presentation and organization."
msgstr ""
"Elementer hjælper med at strukturere og præsentere indhold effektivt. De "
"spænder fra tekstbaserede komponenter som :ref:`titler <website/elements/"
"titles>`, :ref:`lister <website/elements/lists>` og :ref:`tekstfremhævelser "
"<website/elements/text_highlights>` til interaktive som :ref:`knapper "
"<website/elements/buttons>` og :ref:`links <website/elements/links>`. "
"Visuelle elementer som :ref:`billeder <website/elements/"
"images>`, :ref:`ikoner <website/elements/icons>`, :ref:`videoer <website/"
"elements/videos>` og :ref:`animationer <website/elements/animations>` kan "
"også tilføjes for at forbedre indholdspræsentation og organisering."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:13
msgid "To add or modify a website element:"
msgstr "For at tilføje eller ændre et hjemmesideelement:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:15
msgid "Navigate to the relevant website page and click on :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til den relevante hjemmesideside, og klik på :guilabel:`rediger`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:16
msgid ""
"Click the section on the page where you want to add or modify an element."
msgstr ""
"Klik på sektionen på siden, hvor du vil tilføje eller ændre et element."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:17
msgid "Make the necessary changes."
msgstr "Foretag de nødvendige ændringer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:18
msgid "Click on :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:21
msgid ""
"The default styles for headings, buttons, links, and paragraph text, for "
"example, are defined in the :doc:`Theme tab <themes>` of the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Standardstilene for overskrifter, knapper, links og afsnitstekst er f.eks. "
"defineret i :doc:`Tema-fanen <themes>` i hjemmesideredigeringen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:None
msgid "Type / to add website elements."
msgstr "Skriv / for at tilføje hjemmesideelementer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:30
msgid "Titles"
msgstr "Titler"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:32
msgid ""
"Titles define headings and organize website content into different levels "
"for clarity and structure. To insert a title, type `/title`, choose the "
"heading style (:guilabel:`Heading 1`, :guilabel:`Heading 2`, "
"or :guilabel:`Heading 3`), and type the text."
msgstr ""
"Titler definerer overskrifter og organiserer hjemmesidens indhold i "
"forskellige niveauer for klarhed og struktur. For at indsætte en titel skal "
"du skrive `/title`, vælge overskriftsstilen (:guilabel:`Overskrift "
"1`, :guilabel:`Overskrift 2` eller :guilabel:`Overskrift 3`) og skrive "
"teksten."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:37
msgid ""
"Alternatively, type the text, select it, and choose the appropriate style "
"from the :guilabel:`Inline Text` section in the :guilabel:`Customize` tab of "
"the website editor. Additional formatting options, such as fonts and colors, "
"are also available in this section."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan du skrive teksten, markere den og vælge den passende stil "
"fra sektionen :guilabel:`Inlinetekst` i fanen :guilabel:`Tilpas` i "
"hjemmesideredigeringen. Yderligere formateringsmuligheder, såsom skrifttyper "
"og farver, er også tilgængelige i denne sektion."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:46
msgid ""
"Buttons are interactive elements that allow to link to another page or to a "
"page anchor. To insert a button:"
msgstr ""
"Knapper er interaktive elementer, der gør det muligt at linke til en anden "
"side eller til et sideanker. Sådan indsætter du en knap:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:49
msgid "Type `/button`."
msgstr "Skriv `/button`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:50
msgid "Enter the button's label in the :guilabel:`Link Label` field."
msgstr "Indtast knappens etiket i feltet :guilabel:`Linketiket`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:51
msgid ""
"Add the :guilabel:`URL or Email`. Type `/` to search for a page and `#` to "
"link to an anchor."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj :guilabel:`URL eller e-mail`. Skriv `/` for at søge efter en side og "
"`#` for at linke til et anker."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:52
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Style`, :guilabel:`Size`, and :guilabel:`Layout` to "
"define the button's appearance."
msgstr ""
"Indstil :guilabel:`Stil`, :guilabel:`Størrelse` og :guilabel:`Layout` for at "
"definere knappens udseende."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:54
msgid ""
"If needed, toggle the switch to open the linked page or anchor in a new tab."
msgstr ""
"Om nødvendigt skal du skifte kontakten for at åbne den linkede side eller "
"det linkede anker i en ny fane."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:55
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Apply` to save changes."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Anvend` for at gemme ændringer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:58
msgid ""
"To modify an existing button, click the button and edit the options in "
"the :guilabel:`Inline text` section of the website editor."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre en eksisterende knap skal du klikke på knappen og redigere "
"indstillingerne i sektionen :guilabel:`Inlinetekst` i hjemmesideredigeringen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:66
msgid "To insert an image:"
msgstr "Sådan indsætter du et billede:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:68
msgid "Type `/image`."
msgstr "Skriv `/image`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:69
msgid ""
":doc:`Search the Unsplash database </applications/general/integrations/"
"unsplash>` or click :guilabel:`Upload an image` to choose a file from your "
"local images."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Søg i Unsplash-databasen </applications/general/integrations/"
"unsplash>`, eller klik på :guilabel:`Upload et billede` for at vælge en fil "
"fra dine lokale billeder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:71
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:72
msgid ""
"To customize the image, click on the image and edit the options in "
"the :guilabel:`Image` section of the website editor. For example:"
msgstr ""
"For at tilpasse billedet skal du klikke på billedet og redigere "
"indstillingerne i sektionen :guilabel:`Billede` i hjemmesideredigeringen. "
"For eksempel:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:75
msgid ":guilabel:`Replace` the image."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Erstat` billedet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:76
msgid ""
"Define an `alt tag <https://help.siteimprove.com/support/solutions/articles/"
"80000448480-where-are-alt-tags- used-and-why-are-they-important>`_ in "
"the :guilabel:`Description` field."
msgstr ""
"Definer et `alt tag <https://help.siteimprove.com/support/solutions/articles/"
"80000448480-where-are-alt-tags- used-and-why-are-they-important>`_ i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Beskrivelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:78
msgid ""
"Enter a title tag in the :guilabel:`Tooltip` field. This text will appear "
"when visitors hover their mouse over the image."
msgstr ""
"Indtast en titeltag i feltet :guilabel:`Værktøjstip`. Denne tekst vises, når "
"besøgende holder musen over billedet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:80
msgid ""
"Add a :guilabel:`Shape`; some shapes also allow for color customization."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj en :guilabel:`Form`; nogle former tillader også farvetilpasning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:81
msgid ""
"Adjust the image's :guilabel:`Width`, e.g., to improve performance. A "
"smaller size may be suggested if it is sufficient for display."
msgstr ""
"Juster billedets :guilabel:`Bredde`, f.eks. for at forbedre ydeevnen. En "
"mindre størrelse kan foreslås, hvis den er tilstrækkelig til visning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:83
msgid "Resize the image using the :guilabel:`Transform` tool."
msgstr ""
"Tilpas billedets størrelse ved hjælp af værktøjet :guilabel:`Transformer`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:84
msgid ""
"Adjust the :guilabel:`Padding` to add space (in pixels) around the image."
msgstr ""
"Juster :guilabel:`Afstand` for at tilføje plads (i pixels) omkring billedet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:85
msgid "Etc."
msgstr "Osv."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:90
msgid "Videos"
msgstr "Videoer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:92
msgid ""
"To add a video, type `/video`, insert the URL, and turn on the desired "
"options:"
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en video skal du skrive `/video`, indsætte URL'en og slå de "
"ønskede indstillinger til:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Autoplay`: to automatically play the video when the page is "
"accessed. The video is automatically muted by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Autoafspil`: for automatisk at afspille videoen, når siden "
"tilgås. Videoen slås automatisk fra som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:96
msgid ":guilabel:`Loop`: to play the video on a loop."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Gentag`: for at afspille videoen i loop."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:97
msgid ":guilabel:`Hide player controls`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skjul afspillerkontroller`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:98
msgid ":guilabel:`Hide fullscreen button`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skjul fuldskærmsknap`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:99
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Start at`: to define the timestamp where the video should start, "
"in `MM:SS` format."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Start ved`: til at definere tidsstemplet, hvor videoen skal "
"starte, i `MM:SS`-format."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:104
msgid "Icons"
msgstr "Ikoner"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:106
msgid ""
"To insert an icon, type `/image`, go to the :guilabel:`Icons` tab, select an "
"icon, and click :guilabel:`Add`. To modify an icon, click on it and use "
"the :guilabel:`Icon` section of the website editor to customize options, "
"such as :guilabel:`Color`, :guilabel:`Size`, :ref:`Animations <website/"
"elements/animations>`, :guilabel:`Shape`, etc."
msgstr ""
"For at indsætte et ikon skal du skrive `/image`, gå til "
"fanen :guilabel:`Ikoner`, vælge et ikon og klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj`. For "
"at ændre et ikon skal du klikke på det og bruge sektionen :guilabel:`Ikon` i "
"hjemmesideeditoren til at tilpasse indstillinger, "
"såsom :guilabel:`Farve`, :guilabel:`Størrelse`, :ref:`Animationer <website/"
"elements/animations>`, :guilabel:`Form`, osv."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:114
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:190
msgid "Links"
msgstr "Links"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:116
msgid ""
"Links are used to connect different pages and resources, guiding visitors "
"and improving navigation. To add a link, type `/link`, then, in the pop-up "
"that opens, enter the link's :guilabel:`Label` and add the :guilabel:`URL or "
"Email`. Type `/` to search for a page and `#` to link to an :ref:`anchor "
"<website/building_blocks/anchor>`."
msgstr ""
"Links bruges til at forbinde forskellige sider og ressourcer, guide "
"besøgende og forbedre navigationen. For at tilføje et link skal du skrive `/"
"link`, derefter indtaste linkets :guilabel:`Etiket` i pop-up-vinduet, der "
"åbnes, og tilføje :guilabel:`URL eller e-mail`. Skriv `/` for at søge efter "
"en side og `#` for at linke til et :ref:`anker <website/building_blocks/"
"anchor>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:122
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Style` field is set to :guilabel:`Link`. Select a "
"different style to transform the link into a :ref:`button <website/elements/"
"buttons>`."
msgstr ""
"Som standard er feltet :guilabel:`Stil` indstillet til :guilabel:`Link`. "
"Vælg en anden stil for at omdanne linket til en :ref:`knap <website/elements/"
"buttons>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:128
msgid "Lists"
msgstr "Lister"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:130
msgid ""
"Lists help organize content clearly, making information easier to read and "
"improving web pages' structures. Type `/list` and choose from three "
"different types of lists: :guilabel:`Bulleted lists`, :guilabel:`Numbered "
"lists`, or :guilabel:`Checklists`."
msgstr ""
"Lister hjælper med at organisere indhold tydeligt, gøre information lettere "
"at læse og forbedre websiders strukturer. Skriv `/list` og vælg mellem tre "
"forskellige typer lister: :guilabel:`Punktlister`, :guilabel:`Nummererede "
"lister` eller :guilabel:`Tjeklister`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:137
msgid "Text highlights"
msgstr "Tekstfremhævninger"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:139
msgid ""
"Highlights can be added to titles and text using in the :guilabel:`Inline "
"Text` section of the website editor. To add a highlight:"
msgstr ""
"Fremhævninger kan tilføjes til titler og tekst ved hjælp af "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Indlejret tekst` i hjemmesideeditoren. For at tilføje "
"en fremhævning:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:142
msgid "Select the text or title you want to highlight."
msgstr "Vælg den tekst eller titel, du vil fremhæve."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:143
msgid "In the website editor, click on :guilabel:`Highlight`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Fremhæv` i hjemmesideeditoren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:144
msgid "Select the highlight style."
msgstr "Vælg fremhævningsstil."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:145
msgid "Modify its :guilabel:`Color`."
msgstr "Tilpas dens :guilabel:`farve`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:146
msgid "Choose its :guilabel:`Thickness`."
msgstr "Vælg dens :guilabel:`tykkelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:None
msgid "Highlight texts and titles"
msgstr "Fremhæve tekster og overskrifter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:154
msgid "Animations"
msgstr "Animeringer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:156
msgid ""
"Animations are used to add movement to :doc:`building blocks "
"<building_blocks>` and website elements such as images and text. Three types "
"of animation are available: :guilabel:`On Scroll`, :guilabel:`On "
"Appearance`, and :guilabel:`On Hover` (for images only)."
msgstr ""
"Animationer bruges til at tilføje bevægelse til :doc:`byggeblokke "
"<building_blocks>` og hjemmesideelementer såsom billeder og tekst. Tre typer "
"animationer er tilgængelige: :guilabel:`ved rulning`, :guilabel:`ved "
"synlighed` og :guilabel:`ved museover` (kun til billeder)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:160
msgid "To add an animation to a website element:"
msgstr "Sådan tilføjes en animation til et hjemmesideelement:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:162
msgid "Click on the element."
msgstr "Klik på elementet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the website editor, go to the relevant section for the element "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Button`, :guilabel:`Column`, :guilabel:`Inline Text`, "
"etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Gå i hjemmesideeditoren til den relevante sektion for elementet "
"(f.eks. :guilabel:`knap`, :guilabel:`kolonne`, :guilabel:`inline-tekst` "
"osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:165
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Animation` field, select the desired animation type."
msgstr "Vælg i feltet :guilabel:`animation` den ønskede animationstype."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:166
msgid ""
"Customize the animation settings as needed. Available options vary based on "
"the selected animation type."
msgstr ""
"Tilpas animationsindstillingerne efter behov. Tilgængelige indstillinger "
"varierer afhængigt af den valgte animationstype."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:170
msgid "Animations on scroll"
msgstr "Animationer ved rulning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:172
msgid "For animations on scroll, it is possible to:"
msgstr "For animationer ved rulning er det muligt at:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:174
msgid ""
"Choose :guilabel:`In` to add the animation when the element enters the "
"screen and :guilabel:`Out` to add it when it leaves the screen."
msgstr ""
"Vælg :guilabel:`ind` for at tilføje animationen, når elementet kommer ind på "
"skærmen, og :guilabel:`ud` for at tilføje den, når det forlader skærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:176
msgid "Select an :guilabel:`Effect`."
msgstr "Vælg en :guilabel:`effekt`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:177
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:188
msgid "Choose the :guilabel:`Direction` of the effect."
msgstr "Vælg :guilabel:`retning` for effekten."

