msgstr "vælge :icon:`fa-ban` :guilabel:`Ingen`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:36
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save` to apply the changes to the website."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Gem` for at anvende ændringerne på hjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:41
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Farver"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:43
msgid ""
"Odoo's website editor features two main types of colors: :ref:`theme colors "
"<website/themes/theme-colors>` and :ref:`status colors <website/themes/"
"status-colors>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoos hjemmesideeditor indeholder to hovedtyper af farver: :ref:`temafarver "
"<website/themes/theme-colors>` og :ref:`statusfarver <website/themes/status-"
"colors>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:49
msgid "Theme colors"
msgstr "Temafarver"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:51
msgid ""
"Theme colors refer to the set of colors displayed across all pages of the "
"website. They consist of five colors: three :guilabel:`Main` colors, used "
"mainly for buttons and links, and two :guilabel:`Light & Dark` colors, used "
"mainly for text and headings."
msgstr ""
"Temafarver refererer til det sæt af farver, der vises på tværs af alle sider "
"på hjemmesiden. De består af fem farver: tre :guilabel:`Hoved`farver, der "
"hovedsageligt bruges til knapper og links, og to :guilabel:`Lyse og mørke` "
"farver, der hovedsageligt bruges til tekst og overskrifter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:55
msgid ""
"To edit the website's colors, navigate to the :guilabel:`Colors` section of "
"the :guilabel:`Theme` tab. Then:"
msgstr ""
"For at redigere hjemmesidens farver skal du navigere til sektionen "
":guilabel:`Farver` under fanen :guilabel:`Tema`. Derefter:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:58
msgid ""
"Click the color you want to change, then select a "
"predefined :guilabel:`Solid` color or click :guilabel:`Custom` to pick a "
"specific color tone manually (or add its #HEX or RGBA code). Click :icon:`fa-"
"trash` (:guilabel:`Delete`) to remove the color selection."
msgstr ""
"Klik på den farve, du vil ændre, og vælg derefter en foruddefineret "
":guilabel:`Ensfarvet` farve, eller klik på :guilabel:`Brugerdefineret` for "
"at vælge en bestemt farvetone manuelt (eller tilføj dens #HEX- eller RGBA-"
"kode). Klik på :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`Slet`) for at fjerne farvevalget."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:61
msgid ""
"Click the paint palette icon and choose a color palette. As a result, all "
"color customizations are reset."
msgstr ""
"Klik på malepaletikonen og vælg en farvepalet. Som følge heraf nulstilles "
"alle farvetilpasninger."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:64
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically creates :guilabel:`Color Presets` for the chosen colors "
"or palette. These predefined color combinations are applied to various "
"elements of the website to create a structured and visually appealing "
"design. When selecting a color palette, its presets define how those colors "
"are distributed across different elements. To modify them, "
"click :guilabel:`Color Presets`, then select a preset to open the "
"customization dropdown. Each color preset contains colors for the building "
"block’s :guilabel:`Background`, :guilabel:`Text`, :guilabel:`Headings`, :guilabel:`Links`, :guilabel:`Primary "
"Buttons`, and :guilabel:`Secondary Buttons`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo opretter automatisk :guilabel:`Farveforudindstillinger` for de valgte "
"farver eller palet. Disse foruddefinerede farvekombinationer anvendes på "
"forskellige elementer på hjemmesiden for at skabe et struktureret og visuelt "
"tiltalende design. Når du vælger en farvepalet, definerer dens "
"forudindstillinger, hvordan disse farver fordeles på tværs af forskellige "
"elementer. For at ændre dem skal du klikke på "
":guilabel:`Farveforudindstillinger` og derefter vælge en forudindstilling "
"for at åbne tilpasningsdropdownen. Hver farveforudindstilling indeholder "
"farver til byggeklodsens :guilabel:`Baggrund`, :guilabel:`Tekst`, "
":guilabel:`Overskrifter`, :guilabel:`Links`, :guilabel:`Primære knapper` og "
":guilabel:`Sekundære knapper`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:73
msgid ""
"To apply a color preset to a building block, select the building block, go "
"to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, click the color dot located next "
"to :guilabel:`Background`, and choose a :guilabel:`Theme`."
msgstr ""
"For at anvende en farveforudindstilling på en byggeklods skal du vælge "
"byggeklodsen, gå til fanen :guilabel:`Stil`, klikke på farveprikken ved "
"siden af :guilabel:`Baggrund` og vælge et :guilabel:`Tema`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:78
msgid ""
"Changing a color preset automatically updates the colors of both the default "
"preset and the building blocks that use it."
msgstr ""
"Ændring af en farvepræindstilling opdaterer automatisk farverne for både "
"standardpræindstillingen og de byggeklodser, der bruger den."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:84
msgid "Status colors"
msgstr "Statusfarver"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:86
msgid ""
"Status colors indicate the status of certain actions "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Success`, :guilabel:`Warning`, etc.). They're used in pop-"
"up messages that appear to provide feedback to users and website visitors. "
"To customize the website's :guilabel:`Status Colors`, scroll down to "
"the :ref:`Advanced <website/themes/advanced>` section and click the dots to "
"change their color."
msgstr ""
"Statusfarver angiver status for visse handlinger (f.eks. "
":guilabel:`Success`, :guilabel:`Warning` osv.). De bruges i pop op-beskeder, "
"der vises for at give feedback til brugere og hjemmesidebesøgende. For at "
"tilpasse hjemmesidens :guilabel:`Status Colors` skal du rulle ned til "
"sektionen :ref:`Advanced <website/themes/advanced>` og klikke på prikkerne "
"for at ændre deres farve."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:93
msgid ""
"Information related to a successful action on the website appears "
"in :icon:`oi-green-dot` green."
msgstr ""
"Oplysninger relateret til en vellykket handling på hjemmesiden vises i "
":icon:`oi-green-dot` grønt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:0
msgid "Status color selection"
msgstr "Valg af statusfarve"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:0
msgid "Success pop-up"
msgstr "Pop op med succes"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:104
msgid "Fonts"
msgstr "Skrifttyper"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:106
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to customize the font family and font size of website "
"elements, including :ref:`paragraphs and headings <website/themes/paragraphs-"
"headings>`, :ref:`buttons <website/themes/button-styles>`, and :ref:`input "
"fields <website/themes/input-fields>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo giver dig mulighed for at tilpasse skrifttypefamilie og skriftstørrelse "
"for hjemmesideelementer, herunder :ref:`afsnit og overskrifter <website/"
"themes/paragraphs-headings>`, :ref:`knapper <website/themes/button-styles>` "
"og :ref:`inputfelter <website/themes/input-fields>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Font Size`: In "
"the :guilabel:`Paragraph`, :guilabel:`Headings`, :guilabel:`Button`, "
"and :guilabel:`Input Fields` sections, use the :guilabel:`Font Size` field "
"to set a default size. Click the :icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`Toggle "
"more options`) icon to expand the section and define custom sizes (e.g., "
"based on the heading level, button size, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Font Size`: I sektionerne :guilabel:`Paragraph`, "
":guilabel:`Headings`, :guilabel:`Button` og :guilabel:`Input Fields` skal du "
"bruge feltet :guilabel:`Font Size` til at indstille en standardstørrelse. "
"Klik på ikonet :icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`Toggle more options`) for "
"at udvide sektionen og definere brugerdefinerede størrelser (f.eks. baseret "
"på overskriftsniveau, knapstørrelse osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:116
msgid ""
"When :guilabel:`System Fonts` is selected, Odoo uses the native fonts "
"already installed on the visitor's operating system. For example, Android "
"uses **Roboto** as its default system font."
msgstr ""
"Når :guilabel:`System Fonts` er valgt, bruger Odoo de native skrifttyper, "
"der allerede er installeret på besøgendes operativsystem. For eksempel "
"bruger Android **Roboto** som sin standardsystemskrifttype."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Font Family`: In the :guilabel:`Paragraph`, :guilabel:`Headings`, "
"and :guilabel:`Button` sections, select a font from the dropdown menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skrifttypefamilie`: I "
"afsnittene :guilabel:`Afsnit`, :guilabel:`Overskrifter` og :guilabel:`Knap` "
"skal du vælge en skrifttype fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:123
msgid "Custom fonts"
msgstr "Brugerdefinerede skrifttyper"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:125
msgid ""
"To add a custom font not available by default in Odoo, click "
"the :guilabel:`Font Family` dropdown and select :guilabel:`Add a Custom "
"Font` at the bottom. In the :guilabel:`Add a Google font or upload a custom "
"font` pop-up:"
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en brugerdefineret skrifttype, der ikke er tilgængelig som "
"standard i Odoo, skal du klikke på rullemenuen :guilabel:`Font Family` og "
"vælge :guilabel:`Add a Custom Font` nederst. I pop op'en :guilabel:`Add a "
"Google font or upload a custom font`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:129
msgid ""
"To add a Google font, open the :guilabel:`Select a Google Font` dropdown and "
"select the desired font. Toggle off the :guilabel:`Serve font from Google "
"servers` if your website is operated from a location where regulations "
"require compliance with laws such as, but not limited to, the European "
"Union's GDPR. This will ensure the Google Font is stored on the website's "
"server rather than on Google's servers."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en Google-skrifttype skal du åbne rullemenuen "
":guilabel:`Select a Google Font` og vælge den ønskede skrifttype. Slå "
":guilabel:`Serve font from Google servers` fra, hvis din hjemmeside drives "
"fra et sted, hvor regler kræver overholdelse af love såsom, men ikke "
"begrænset til, EU's GDPR. Dette vil sikre, at Google-skrifttypen gemmes på "
"hjemmesidens server i stedet for på Googles servere."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:134
msgid ""
"To upload a :guilabel:`Custom Font` from your computer, "
"click :guilabel:`Choose File`."
msgstr ""
"For at uploade en :guilabel:`Custom Font` fra din computer skal du klikke på "
":guilabel:`Choose File`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:136
msgid "Once done, click :guilabel:`Save and Reload`."
msgstr "Når du er færdig, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Save and Reload`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:139
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Preview` of the selected font is displayed on the right side of "
"the window."
msgstr ""
"En :guilabel:`Preview` af den valgte skrifttype vises i højre side af "
"vinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:142
msgid "Styles"
msgstr "Stilarter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:144
msgid ""
"The appearance of website elements can be further customized. For example, "
"you can customize :ref:`paragraphs and headings <website/themes/paragraphs-"
"headings>`, :ref:`buttons <website/themes/button-styles>`, :ref:`links "
"<website/themes/link-style>`, and :ref:`input fields <website/themes/input-"
"fields>`."
msgstr ""
"Udseendet af hjemmesideelementer kan tilpasses yderligere. For eksempel kan "
"du tilpasse :ref:`afsnit og overskrifter <website/themes/paragraphs-headings>"
"`, :ref:`knapper <website/themes/button-styles>`, :ref:`links <website/"
"themes/link-style>` og :ref:`inputfelter <website/themes/input-fields>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:152
msgid "Paragraphs & headings"
msgstr "Afsnit og overskrifter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:154
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Paragraph` and :guilabel:`Headings` sections offer additional "
"styling options for these text elements. You can:"
msgstr ""
"Sektionerne :guilabel:`Paragraph` og :guilabel:`Headings` tilbyder "
"yderligere stileringsmuligheder for disse tekstelementer. Du kan:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:157
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:174
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:208
msgid "Modify the :ref:`font settings <website/themes/fonts>`."
msgstr "Ændre :ref:`skrifttypeindstillingerne <website/themes/fonts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:158
msgid ""
"Adjust the :guilabel:`Line Height` to define the spacing between lines of "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Justere :guilabel:`Line Height` for at definere afstanden mellem tekstlinjer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:159
msgid ""
"Adjust :guilabel:`Margins` to define the spacing around paragraphs and "
"headings."
msgstr ""
"Justere :guilabel:`Margins` for at definere afstanden omkring afsnit og "
"overskrifter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:166
msgid ""
"To customize the style of the website's primary and secondary buttons, "
"navigate to the :guilabel:`Button` section and edit the relevant options:"
msgstr ""
"For at tilpasse stilen for hjemmesidens primære og sekundære knapper skal du "
"navigere til sektionen :guilabel:`Button` og redigere de relevante "
"muligheder:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:169
msgid ""
"Open the :icon:`fa-caret-down` dropdown menu next to the :guilabel:`Primary "
"Style` or :guilabel:`Secondary Style` fields to change the style for each "
"button type, such as :guilabel:`Fill`, :guilabel:`Outline`, "
"or :guilabel:`Flat`. When selecting :guilabel:`Outline`, "
"the :guilabel:`Border Width` option appears below, allowing you to adjust "
"the width of the button's outline."
msgstr ""
"Åbn rullemenuen :icon:`fa-caret-down` ved siden af felterne "
":guilabel:`Primary Style` eller :guilabel:`Secondary Style` for at ændre "
"stilen for hver knaptype, såsom :guilabel:`Fill`, :guilabel:`Outline` eller "
":guilabel:`Flat`. Når du vælger :guilabel:`Outline`, vises muligheden "
":guilabel:`Border Width` nedenfor, som giver dig mulighed for at justere "
"bredden af knappens kontur."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:175
msgid ""
"Adjust the :guilabel:`Padding` to change the spacing around the buttons' "
"labels."
msgstr ""
"Juster :guilabel:`Padding`, for at ændre afstanden omkring knappernes "
"etiketter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:176
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Round Corners` option to adjust the buttons' border "
"radius."
msgstr ""
"Brug indstillingen :guilabel:`Round Corners` til at justere knappernes "
"kantradius."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:177
msgid ""
"Add an animation when a button is clicked in the :guilabel:`On Click Effect` "
"dropdown menu."
msgstr ""
"Přidejte animaci při kliknutí na tlačítko v rozbalovací "
"nabídce :guilabel:`On Click Effect`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:None
msgid "Primary and secondary buttons"
msgstr "Primární a sekundární tlačítka"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:183
msgid ""
