msgid "Input fields"
msgstr "Inputfelter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:204
msgid ""
"To customize the style of the website's input fields, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Input Fields` section and edit the relevant options:"
msgstr ""
"For at tilpasse stilen af hjemmesidens inputfelter skal du navigere til "
