#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:207
msgid "Adjust the :guilabel:`Padding` to change the spacing around the fields."
msgstr "Juster :guilabel:`Padding`, for at ændre afstanden omkring felterne."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:209
msgid "Customize the :guilabel:`Border Width` around fields."
msgstr "Tilpas :guilabel:`Border Width` omkring felter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:210
msgid "Define a :guilabel:`Border Radius` to round the fields' corners."
msgstr "Definer en :guilabel:`Border Radius` for at runde felters hjørner."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:211
msgid ""
"Choose a :guilabel:`Background` :ref:`color <website/themes/colors>` to fill "
"the fields."
msgstr ""
"Vælg en :guilabel:`Background`-:ref:`farve <website/themes/colors>` til at "
"udfylde felterne."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:216
msgid "Advanced settings"
msgstr "Avancerede indstillinger"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:218
msgid ""
"Additional settings can be configured in the :guilabel:`Advanced` section, "
"such as :doc:`showing or hiding the header <../structure/header_footer>`, "
"using :guilabel:`Code Injection` for :ref:`website verification through an "
"HTML tag <website/google_search_console/HTML-tag>`, and "
"configuring :ref:`status colors <website/themes/status-colors>` "
"and :guilabel:`Grays`."
msgstr ""
"Yderligere indstillinger kan konfigureres i sektionen :guilabel:`Advanced`, "
"såsom :doc:`visning eller skjulning af headeren <../structure/header_footer>"
"`, brug af :guilabel:`Code Injection` til :ref:`hjemmesideverifikation "
"gennem et HTML-tag <website/google_search_console/HTML-tag>`, og "
"konfigurering af :ref:`statusfarver <website/themes/status-colors>` og "
":guilabel:`Grays`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:223
msgid ""
"You can also configure Google Maps to display maps and enable geolocation "
"features on the website, e.g., on the :guilabel:`Contact Us` page and in "
"specific snippets. To configure this option:"
msgstr ""
"Du kan også konfigurere Google Maps til at vise kort og aktivere "
"geolokaliseringsfunktioner på hjemmesiden, f.eks. på siden "
":guilabel:`Contact Us` og i specifikke snippets. For at konfigurere denne "
"indstilling:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:227
msgid ""
"Go to your `Google account <https://console.cloud.google.com/getting-"
"started>`_."
msgstr ""
"Gå til din `Google-konto <https://console.cloud.google.com/getting-started>"
"`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:228
msgid ""
":ref:`Enable <address_autocomplete/enable-api>` the :guilabel:`Maps Static "
"API`, :guilabel:`Maps JavaScript API`, and :guilabel:`Places API`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Aktiver <address_autocomplete/enable-api>` :guilabel:`Maps Static "
"API`, :guilabel:`Maps JavaScript API` og :guilabel:`Places API`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:232
msgid ""
"Do not enable :guilabel:`Places API (New)`, as it is not yet supported by "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Aktiver ikke :guilabel:`Places API (New)`, da det endnu ikke understøttes af "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:233
msgid ""
"Using the Google APIs could require `payment to Google <https://"
"mapsplatform.google.com/pricing/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Brug af Google API'erne kan kræve `betaling til Google <https://"
"mapsplatform.google.com/pricing/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:236
msgid ""
":ref:`Create an API key <address_autocomplete/generate_api_key>` and copy it."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Opret en API-nøgle <address_autocomplete/generate_api_key>`, og kopiér "
"den."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:237
msgid ""
"In Odoo's website editor, go to the :guilabel:`Theme` tab, and, in "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced` section, click :guilabel:`Custom Key` next "
"to :guilabel:`Google Map`."
msgstr ""
"I Odoos hjemmesideeditor skal du gå til fanen :guilabel:`Tema` og i "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Avanceret` klikke på :guilabel:`Brugerdefineret nøgle` "
"ved siden af :guilabel:`Google Map`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/themes.rst:239
msgid "Paste the generated API key into the :guilabel:`API Key` field."
msgstr "Indsæt den genererede API-nøgle i feltet :guilabel:`API-nøgle`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:5
msgid "You can choose to display or hide building blocks based on a visitor's:"
msgstr ""
"Můžete zvolit zobrazení nebo skrytí stavebních bloků na základě "
"návštěvníkova:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:7
msgid "device type (mobile or computer),"
msgstr "typu zařízení (mobilní nebo počítač),"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:8
msgid "country (IP-based geolocation),"
msgstr "země (geolokace na základě IP adresy),"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:9
msgid "website language,"
msgstr "jazyka webu,"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`UTM parameters <../reporting/link_tracker>`, and"
msgstr ":doc:`UTM parametrů <../reporting/link_tracker>` a"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:11
msgid "login state."
msgstr "stavu přihlášení."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:16
msgid "Mobile/computer"
msgstr "Mobilní/počítač"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:25
msgid ""
"To toggle the visibility of a building block based on the visitor's device "
"type:"
msgstr ""
"Pro přepnutí viditelnosti stavebního bloku na základě typu zařízení "
"návštěvníka:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:27
msgid "Open the website editor and select a block."
msgstr "Otevřete editor webu a vyberte blok."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:28
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, under the block's customization options, "
"look for :guilabel:`Visibility`."
msgstr ""
"Na kartě :guilabel:`Přizpůsobit` v možnostech přizpůsobení bloku "
"vyhledejte :guilabel:`Viditelnost`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:31
msgid ""
"Click the |desktop icon| (:guilabel:`Show/Hide on Desktop`) button to hide "
"the block for users visiting your website from a computer."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na tlačítko |desktop icon| (:guilabel:`Zobrazit/Skrýt na počítači`) "
"pro skrytí bloku pro uživatele navštěvující vaši webovou stránku z počítače."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:33
msgid ""
"Click the |mobile icon| (:guilabel:`Show/Hide on Mobile`) button to hide the "
"block for users visiting your website from a mobile device."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na tlačítko |mobile icon| (:guilabel:`Zobrazit/Skrýt na mobilu`) "
"pro skrytí bloku pro uživatele navštěvující vaši webovou stránku z mobilního "
"zařízení."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:36
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:83
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save` to apply the changes."
msgstr "Klikněte na :guilabel:`Uložit` pro použití změn."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:38
msgid ""
"It is also sometimes possible to hide elements within blocks. It is mostly "
"used to hide specific elements inside blocks that may be too wide to be "
"correctly displayed on mobile devices. To see if the option is available, "
"select an element within a block and look for the :guilabel:`Visibility` "
"option under the element's customization option."
msgstr ""
"Někdy je také možné skrýt prvky uvnitř bloků. Používá se to především ke "
"skrytí specifických prvků uvnitř bloků, které mohou být příliš široké na "
"správné zobrazení na mobilních zařízeních. Chcete-li zjistit, zda je možnost "
"dostupná, vyberte prvek uvnitř bloku a vyhledejte "
"možnost :guilabel:`Viditelnost` v možnostech přizpůsobení prvku."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:44
msgid "The selected image is hidden on mobile devices."
msgstr "Vybraný obrázek je skrytý na mobilních zařízeních."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:0
msgid "Example of an column element hidden on mobile devices"
msgstr "Příklad prvku sloupce skrytého na mobilních zařízeních"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:52
msgid "Conditions"
msgstr "Betingelser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:54
msgid ""
"To access the country, website language, UTM parameters, and login state "
"conditions:"
msgstr ""
"Pro přístup k podmínkám země, jazyka webové stránky, UTM parametrů a stavu "
"přihlášení:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:56
msgid "Open the website editor and select a building block."
msgstr "Otevřete editor webových stránek a vyberte stavební blok."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:57
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, look for :guilabel:`Visibility`."
msgstr "Na kartě :guilabel:`Přizpůsobit` vyhledejte :guilabel:`Viditelnost`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:58
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`No condition` and select :guilabel:`Conditionally` instead "
"to display the different options:"
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Bez podmínky` a místo toho "
"vyberte :guilabel:`Podmíněně` pro zobrazení různých možností:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:61
msgid ":guilabel:`Country`: the country of the visitor's IP address."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Země`: země IP adresy návštěvníka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:62
msgid ":guilabel:`Languages`: the website language used by the visitor."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jazyky`: jazyk webové stránky používaný návštěvníkem."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:65
msgid ""
"This option is only available if more than one :doc:`language is installed "
"<../configuration/translate>`."
msgstr ""
"Tato možnost je dostupná pouze v případě, že je :doc:`nainstalováno více než "
"jeden jazyk <../configuration/translate>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:68
msgid ":guilabel:`UTM Campaign`: the selected campaign."
msgstr ":guilabel:`UTM kampaň`: vybraná kampaň."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:69
msgid ":guilabel:`UTM Medium`: the selected medium of any campaign."
msgstr ":guilabel:`UTM médium`: vybrané médium jakékoli kampaně."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:70
msgid ":guilabel:`UTM Source`: the selected source of any campaign."
msgstr ":guilabel:`UTM zdroj`: vybraný zdroj jakékoli kampaně."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:71
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Users`: select whether the visitor should be :guilabel:`Logged "
"In` or :guilabel:`Logged Out` to view the block. By default, the option is "
"set to :guilabel:`Visible for Everyone`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uživatelé`: vyberte, zda má být návštěvník :guilabel:`Přihlášen` "
"nebo :guilabel:`Odhlášen`, aby viděl blok. Ve výchozím nastavení je možnost "
"nastavena na :guilabel:`Viditelné pro všechny`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:75
msgid ""
"For one or more of the first five options, choose if the block should "
"be :guilabel:`Visible for` or :guilabel:`Hidden for`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Choose a record...` and select it."
msgstr ""
"Pro jednu nebo více z prvních pěti možností zvolte, zda má být "
"blok :guilabel:`Viditelný pro` nebo :guilabel:`Skrytý pro`, poté klikněte "
"na :guilabel:`Vybrat záznam...` a vyberte ho."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:79
msgid ""
"You can select multiple records for each option by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Choose a record...` again."
msgstr ""
"Můžete vybrat více záznamů pro každou možnost opětovným kliknutím "
"na :guilabel:`Vybrat záznam...`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-minus` (:guilabel:`remove`) button to remove an option."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-minus` (:guilabel:`fjern`) knappen for at fjerne en "
"mulighed."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:86
msgid ""
"A block with the following configuration will only be displayed to visitors "
"with a Belgian IP address, for which the website is displayed in French, "
"unless they visit the page using the `Sales` campaign tracked URL."
msgstr ""
"En blok med følgende konfiguration vil kun blive vist til besøgende med en "
"belgisk IP-adresse, hvor hjemmesiden vises på fransk, medmindre de besøger "
"siden ved hjælp af den sporede URL med `Sales`-kampagnen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:0
msgid "Example of a block configured with several visibility conditions"
msgstr "Eksempel på en blok konfigureret med flere synlighedsbetingelser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:96
msgid "Invisible elements"
msgstr "Usynlige elementer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:98
msgid ""
"Blocks and elements with custom visibility settings are listed at the bottom "
"of the website editor sidebar. You can preview how the page would look like "
"by clicking the :icon:`fa-eye` (:guilabel:`visible`) button to hide a block "
"or element, or the :icon:`fa-eye-slash` (:guilabel:`hidden`) to show it in "
"the website editor."
msgstr ""
"Blokke og elementer med tilpassede synlighedsindstillinger vises nederst i "
"hjemmesideredigeringens sidepanel. Du kan forhåndsvise, hvordan siden vil se "
"ud, ved at klikke på :icon:`fa-eye` (:guilabel:`synlig`) knappen for at "
"skjule en blok eller et element, eller :icon:`fa-eye-slash` "
"(:guilabel:`skjult`) for at vise det i hjemmesideredigeringen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/visibility.rst:None
msgid ""
"Blocks and elements with custom visibility settings displayed at the bottom "
"of the editor"
msgstr ""
"Blokke og elementer med tilpassede synlighedsindstillinger vist nederst i "
"editoren"

