#~ msgid ""
#~ "Link Trackers allow you to track your marketing campaigns (emails, banner "
#~ "ads, blog posts, social media posts, affiliate links, etc.). This way, "
#~ "you are able to identify your best traffic sources and make informed "
#~ "decisions about the distribution of your marketing budget."
