#~ msgid "Configure your eCommerce website"
#~ msgstr "Konfigurer din eHandels hjemmeside"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "eCommerce is a crucial feature in the multi-websites environment. We made "
#~ "it so that the entire flow can be customized to fit the very audience of "
#~ "each website."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "eHandel er en kritisk funktion i multi-virksomheds miljøet. Vi har sørget "
